%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwayanad-to-be-next-amethi-posters-warn-gandhis-on-kerala-chief-minister-pick-11489367%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwayanad-to-be-next-amethi-posters-warn-gandhis-on-kerala-chief-minister-pick-11489367%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22AI's%20newest%20aesthetic%20has%20some%20people%20upset%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20person%20is%20pictured%20shutting%20a%20laptop.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0355b57c7e83f26041acd0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EThai%20Liang%20Lim%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20post%20originally%20appeared%20in%20the%20Business%20Insider%20Today%20newsletter.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cem%3EYou%20can%20sign%20up%20for%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsubscription%2Fnewsletter%2Finsider-today%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBusiness%20Insider's%20daily%20newsletter%20here%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Patagonia%20vest%20is%20to%20a%20finance%20bro%20as%20a%20cracked%20laptop%20is%20to%20an%20AI-agent%20power%20user.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20calling%20card%20for%20AI%20coders%20is%20someone%20who%20won't%20shut%20their%20laptop%2C%20even%20if%20it%20makes%20them%20look%20a%20bit%20silly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20airports%20to%20high%20school%20hallways%20to%20ice%20rinks%2C%20people%20are%20leaving%20their%20laptops%20at%20least%20slightly%20open%20to%20keep%20their%20coding%20agents%20running.%20BI's%20Henry%20Chandonnet%20spoke%20to%20these%20coders%20about%20their%20dedication%20to%20the%20AI%20agent%20game%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcoders-keep-laptops-open-in-public-ai-agent-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ethe%20funny%20interactions%20they've%20had%20as%20a%20result%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20approaches%20may%20differ%20%E2%80%94%20some%20keep%20the%20screen%20wide%20open%20while%20others%20just%20leave%20a%20finger%20in%20between%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20result%20is%20the%20same%3A%20if%20it's%20cracked%2C%20they're%20cooking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20not%20to%20say%20their%20dedication%20doesn't%20come%20with%20a%20bit%20of%20embarrassment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20people%20think%20I'm%20whatever%20the%20equivalent%20of%20an%20iPad%20kid%20is%20for%20a%20middle-aged%20woman%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20AI%20user%20told%20Henry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20can%20almost%20hear%20some%20of%20you%20screaming%3A%20You%20can%20set%20up%20your%20computer%20to%20keep%20running%20when%20the%20screen%20is%20closed!%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20got%20plenty%20of%20comments%20on%20Henry's%20story%20making%20that%20exact%20point.%20(Yes%2C%20you%20can%20comment%20on%20our%20stories.%20Yes%2C%20we%20actually%20read%20them.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Bwell%2C%20actually%26quot%3B%20crowd%20isn't%20wrong.%20There%20are%20a%20number%20of%20ways%20to%20do%20this%2C%20from%20changing%20your%20computer's%20settings%20to%20downloading%20a%20slew%20of%20third-party%20software.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-keep-laptop-ai-agent-running-while-lid-closed-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EHenry%20breaks%20down%20all%20the%20methods%20here%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20comments%20were%20genuinely%20highlighting%20this%20trick.%20Others%2C%20however%2C%20came%20off%20a%20bit%20more%20aggressive%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSeriously%3F!%20It's%20a%20simple%20setting%2C%20power%20options%20generally%2C%20to%20keep%20it%20running%20and%20not%20shut%20down%20when%20closed.%20Coders%3F!%20These%20aren't%20engineers%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20commenter%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20isn't%20that%20the%20point%3F%20The%20AI%20revolution%20has%20largely%20been%20about%20empowering%20non-technical%20people%20to%20code.%20And%20now%20that%20they're%20here%2C%20they%20might%20do%20things%20a%20bit%20differently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20upset%20over%20that%20is%20like%20being%20a%20fan%20of%20an%20indie%20band%20that%20suddenly%20makes%20it%20big%20and%20criticizing%20the%20newcomers%20for%20not%20knowing%20the%20B-side%20tracks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20spirit%20of%20the%20band%20analogy%2C%20coding%20is%20having%20its%20Billboard%20moment.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvibe-coding-becoming-a-real-job-startups-entrepreneurship-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EVibe-coding%20tools%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20turned%20it%20mainstream%2C%20and%20there's%20no%20going%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDoes%20that%20mean%20people%20might%20not%20follow%20old-school%20coding%20etiquette%3F%20Sure%2C%20but%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20it's%20wrong.%20(If%20you%20have%20some%20quirky%20behaviors%20around%20AI%20tools%2C%20or%20have%20noticed%20some%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fform.typeform.com%2Fto%2FLQeh11Ob%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Elet%20us%20know%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20who%20knows%2C%20maybe%20you'll%20learn%20a%20thing%20or%20two%20from%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-trend-laptop-open-crack-agent-power-user-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778673603000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0396aa58810e27922acf89%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-trend-laptop-open-crack-agent-power-user-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22We%20wrote%20about%20AI%20coders%20carrying%20around%20half-open%20laptops%20to%20keep%20their%20AI%20agents%20working%2C%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20you%20crashed%20out%20over%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ddefrancesco%40businessinsider.com%20(Dan%20DeFrancesco)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Roblox%20just%20hired%20an%20Amazon%20exec%20to%20unlock%20its%20next%20phase%20of%20growth%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226108%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Roblox%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a02f206c9dd4cb81cda96e7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224072%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERoblox%20has%20hired%20its%20first-ever%20chief%20growth%20officer.%20The%20company%20has%20set%20out%20a%20long-term%20vision%20to%20capture%2010%25%20of%20the%20global%20gaming%20content%20market.%3Cp%3EJean-Christophe%20VERHAEGEN%20%2F%20AFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ERoblox%20has%20hired%20its%20first-ever%20chief%20growth%20officer.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EJohn%20Ciancutti%20joins%20from%20Amazon%20and%20will%20lead%20its%20discovery%20team%20and%20international%20expansion.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ERoblox%20has%20set%20a%20goal%20of%20capturing%2010%25%20of%20the%20global%20gaming%20content%20market.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ERoblox%20just%20made%20a%20big%20hire%20it%20hopes%20can%20unlock%20its%20next%20stage%20of%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20online%20entertainment%20and%20gaming%20platform%20%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3Eexclusively%20told%20CMO%20Insider%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20it%20had%20appointed%20John%20Ciancutti%20as%20its%20first-ever%20chief%20growth%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECiancutti%20is%20responsible%20for%20Roblox's%20discovery%20team%2C%20which%20works%20on%20its%20TikTok-like%20algorithm%20that%20recommends%20games%20and%20experiences%20to%20users%20most%20likely%20to%20play%20them.%20Roblox%20is%20a%20virtual%20universe%20available%20on%20mobile%20devices%2C%20desktops%2C%20and%20video%20game%20consoles%20that%20allows%20users%20to%20play%20and%20design%20games%20and%20other%20online%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECiancutti%20is%20also%20charged%20with%20leading%20the%20company's%20international%20growth%2C%20including%20its%20expansion%20in%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20joins%20Roblox%20at%20a%20crucial%20moment.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20recently%20lowered%20its%202026%20revenue%20growth%20forecast%20as%20it%20prioritizes%20safety%20improvements%2C%20such%20as%20age-based%20accounts%20and%20mandatory%20age-verification%20checks.%20These%20are%20designed%20to%20limit%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Froblox-online-gaming-giant-child-predator-allegations-lawsuits-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eadult%20interactions%20with%20children%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoblox's%20daily%20active%20user%20count%20fell%20slightly%20to%20132%20million%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%2C%20from%20144%20million%20in%20the%20prior%20quarter%20and%20from%20a%20peak%20of%20152%20million%20earlier%20in%202025.%20Revenue%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%20grew%2039%25%20to%20%241.4%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoblox%20is%20branching%20out%20into%20new%20areas%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Froblox-peter-yang-says-ai-is-coming-for-corporate-life-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epowered%20by%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20betting%20that%20the%20technology%20can%20attract%20a%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrow-a-garden-roblox-robux-why-most-popular-explained-how-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewave%20of%20developers%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20its%20platform.%20Last%20month%2C%20it%20unveiled%20Roblox%20Reality%2C%20a%20new%20initiative%20designed%20to%20help%20creators%20build%20photorealistic%20games%20%E2%80%94%20a%20shift%20from%20the%20blocky%2C%20cartoon-style%20worlds%20that%20have%20long%20defined%20Roblox.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20set%20a%20long-term%20goal%20of%20reaching%201%20billion%20users%20and%20capturing%2010%25%20of%20the%20global%20gaming%20content%20market.%20Roblox%20said%20it%20had%20a%203.4%25%20market%20share%20at%20the%20end%20of%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c931e0ec-23fd-47d9-bc11-8473244d1e0a%5C%22%3ECiancutti%20brings%20product%20experience%20from%20across%20Big%20Tech%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECiancutti%20brings%20a%20wealth%20of%20experience%20in%20building%20consumer%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20most%20recently%20worked%20at%20Amazon%2C%20where%20he%20led%20product%20and%20engineering%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-music%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAmazon%20Music%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Prior%20to%20that%2C%20he%20founded%20the%20personalized%20audio%20news%20service%2060dB%2C%20which%20was%20acquired%20by%20Google%20in%202017%20and%20integrated%20into%20Google%20Audio%20News.%20Later%20at%20Google%2C%20Ciancutti%20held%20senior%20product%20and%20strategy%20roles%20within%20its%20search%20division.%20He%20also%20previously%20worked%20at%20Meta%20and%20Netflix.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECiancutti%20told%20CMO%20Insider%20that%20he%20sees%20future%20growth%20opportunities%20in%20international%20markets%2C%20among%20older%20age%20groups%2C%20and%20in%20a%20more%20diverse%20set%20of%20experiences%20on%20the%20platform.%20Roblox%20said%20last%20month%20that%20users%20over%2018%20represented%2026%25%20of%20its%20US%20daily%20active%20users%20who%20had%20used%20its%20age-checking%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECiancutti%20said%20the%20strength%20of%20Roblox's%20creator%20ecosystem%2C%20which%20includes%20emerging%20developers%20and%20established%20studios%2C%20was%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20he%20was%20drawn%20to%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20stands%20out%20to%20me%20about%20Roblox%20is%20the%20breadth%20of%20what%20the%20platform%20has%20become%20%E2%80%94%20for%20players%2C%20creators%2C%20developers%2C%20and%20brands%20alike%2C%26quot%3B%20Ciancutti%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20there's%20enormous%20potential%20to%20continue%20growing%20awareness%20across%20markets%20and%20audiences%20as%20the%20platform%20evolves.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2217b7f0ad-b76a-4e85-8819-ae5d23a7141f%5C%22%3EWhere%20Roblox's%20next%20growth%20spurts%20could%20come%20from%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMichael%20Pachter%2C%20a%20gaming%20research%20analyst%20at%20Wedbush%20Securities%2C%20said%20in%20order%20to%20grow%20further%20and%20boost%20playing%20hours%20from%20users%2C%20the%20company%20should%20consider%20bringing%20on%20successful%20games%20from%20other%20platforms%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20%26quot%3BFortnite%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BCandy%20Crush%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BLeague%20of%20Legends%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BCall%20of%20Duty%3A%20Warzone%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20onto%20Roblox.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20Roblox%20customers%20who%20play%20these%20other%20games%20on%20other%20platforms%20would%20likely%20migrate%20their%20gameplay%20to%20the%20Roblox%20platform%2C%20allowing%20Roblox%20to%20benefit%20from%20the%20player%20spending%20in%20each%20game%2C%26quot%3B%20Pachter%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdvertising%20is%20another%20major%20growth%20opportunity%2C%20Pachter%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoblox%20first%20introduced%20ads%20in%202023%20and%20has%20steadily%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Froblox-ad-launch-hires-measurement-ecommerce-partnerships-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eexpanded%20the%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20programmatic%20partnerships%20with%20adtech%20giants%20like%20Google%20and%20Amazon%2C%20rewarded%20video%20ads%20that%20give%20users%20in-game%20perks%20for%20watching%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Froblox-gen-z-buy-physical-products-commerce-games-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecommerce%20integrations%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20a%20new%20feature%20that%20lets%20brands%20place%20ads%20on%20the%20Roblox%20homepage.%20Creators%20can%20earn%20a%20share%20of%20ad%20revenue%20from%20their%20games%20in%20the%20form%20of%20Robux%2C%20the%20platform's%20virtual%20currency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPachter%20said%20that%20Roblox%20is%20too%20fixated%20on%20%26quot%3Bseamless%26quot%3B%20experiences%20akin%20to%20product%20placement%20that%20keep%20users%20within%20the%20platform's%20walls%2C%20and%20hasn't%20focused%20enough%20on%20the%20type%20of%20interstitial%20advertising%20found%20elsewhere%20on%20the%20web%2C%20such%20as%20on%20YouTube%20or%20Instagram%20Reels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20a%20multibillion-dollar%20opportunity%20here%2C%20but%20are%20not%20appropriately%20focused%20to%20exploit%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Pachter%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20Ciancutti's%20hire%2C%20Roblox%20said%20this%20week%20it%20had%20appointed%20four%20regional%20general%20managers%20to%20help%20lead%20its%20international%20push%3A%20Joost%20Hagesteijn%20in%20Europe%3B%20Sunil%20Rao%20in%20India%3B%20Diego%20Dzodan%20in%20Latin%20America%3B%20and%20Mohamed%20El%20Sheakh%2C%20who%20will%20lead%20its%20Middle%20East%2C%20North%20Africa%2C%20and%20T%C3%BCrkiye%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Froblox-hires-first-chief-growth-officer-from-amazon-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778673601000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a02f22fba7ef34b41f3746e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Froblox-hires-first-chief-growth-officer-from-amazon-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Roblox%20has%20hired%20its%20first-ever%20chief%20growth%20officer%20as%20it%20builds%20toward%20its%20goal%20of%20capturing%2010%25%20of%20the%20global%20gaming%20content%20market.%22%2C%22auth