and%20Elon%20Musk%20picked%20Jensen%20Huang%20up%20in%20Alaska%20on%20their%20Air%20Force%20One%20trip%20to%20China%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20collage%20of%20Elon%20Musk%20delivers%20a%20speech%20during%20the%20World%20Economic%20Forum%20Annual%20Meeting%20in%20Davos%2C%20Switzerland%2C%20and%20Jensen%20Huang%2C%20speaks%20during%20the%2029th%20annual%20Milken%20Institute%20Global%20Conference%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0457d895396a3b6e417d14%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EElon%20Musk%20and%20Jensen%20Huang%20joined%20Trump%20on%20Air%20Force%20One.%3Cp%3EHarun%20Ozalp%2FAnadolu%20via%20Getty%20Images%3B%20Patrick%20T.%20Fallon%20%2F%20AFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%20is%20heading%20to%20China%20with%20a%20delegation%20of%20at%20least%20a%20dozen%20business%20leaders.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EElon%20Musk%20said%20that%20he%20and%20Jensen%20Huang%20are%20traveling%20on%20Air%20Force%20One.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20CEOs%20of%20Apple%2C%20Boeing%2C%20and%20Goldman%20Sachs%20are%20also%20heading%20to%20China%2C%20Trump%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fbusinessinsider.com%2Felon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Jensen%20Huang%20headed%20to%20China%20on%20Air%20Force%20One.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Tesla%20and%20Nvidia%20CEOs%20are%20part%20of%20the%20delegation%20accompanying%20President%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-tim-cook-trump-xi-jinping-china-ai-tech-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDonald%20Trump%20to%20Beijing%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20touched%20down%20around%208%20p.m.%20local%20time%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20Truth%20Social%2C%20Trump%20named%2010%20other%20business%20leaders%20who%20were%20traveling%20with%20him%2C%20too.%20Although%20in%20an%20X%20post%20during%20the%20flight%2C%20Musk%20said%20he%20and%20Huang%20were%20the%20only%20ones%20on%20board%20the%20presidential%20airplane.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20also%20said%20that%20he%20was%20using%20a%20Starlink%20internet%20connection%2C%20allowing%20him%20to%20post%20from%20over%20the%20Pacific%20Ocean.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20comes%20as%20Tesla%20is%20losing%20ground%20to%20Chinese%20electric-vehicle%20companies.%20In%202025%2C%20BYD%20sold%20more%20battery%20EVs%20than%20Tesla%20for%20the%20first%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20was%20the%20biggest%20donor%20in%20the%202024%20election%2C%20spending%20at%20least%20%24277%20million%20supporting%20Trump%20and%20other%20Republican%20candidates.%20They%20came%20to%20loggerheads%20last%20summer%2C%20as%20Musk%20spoke%20out%20against%20the%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-is-ripping-trumps-big-beautiful-bill-again-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBig%20Beautiful%20Bill%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20and%20floated%20the%20idea%20of%20starting%20a%20new%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20was%20on%20board%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fair-force-one-features%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAir%20Force%20One%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20it%20departed%20Joint%20Base%20Andrews%2C%20according%20to%20a%20White%20House%20pool%20report.%20Huang%20joined%20during%20a%20refueling%20stop%20in%20Anchorage%2C%20Alaska.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Nvidia%20boss%20was%20pictured%20wearing%20a%20backpack%20and%20standing%20on%20the%20tarmac%2C%20in%20an%20X%20post%20shared%20by%20the%20New%20York%20Post's%20White%20House%20correspondent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuang%20has%20long%20been%20trying%20to%20get%20permission%20for%20Nvidia%20to%20sell%20its%20artificial%20intelligence%20chips%20to%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20chip%20company%20CEOs%20on%20the%20trip%20included%20Sanjay%20Mehrotra%20of%20Micron%20and%20Cristiano%20Amon%20of%20Qualcomm%2C%20Trump%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20China%20restricted%20the%20use%20of%20some%20Micron%20chips%20in%20critical%20infrastructure%2C%20citing%20national%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20said%20that%20other%20business%20leaders%20joining%20him%20on%20the%20trip%20included%20Apple's%20Tim%20Cook%2C%20BlackRock's%20Larry%20Fink%2C%20Blackstone's%20Stephen%20Schwarzman%2C%20Boeing's%20Kelly%20Ortberg%2C%20Cargill's%20Brian%20Sikes%2C%20Citi's%20Jane%20Fraser%2C%20GE%20Aerospace's%20Larry%20Culp%2C%20and%20David%20Solomon%20of%20Goldman%20Sachs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChina%20is%20a%20huge%20and%20growing%20market%20for%20commercial%20airplanes%2C%20so%20Ortberg%20may%20be%20hoping%20to%20work%20on%20a%20deal%20with%20the%20country's%20airlines.%20Airbus%2C%20Boeing's%20main%20rival%2C%20last%20month%20signed%20a%20%2421.4%20billion%20deal%20with%20China%20Southern%20Airlines%20and%20its%20subsidiary%20Xiamen%20Airlines%20for%20more%20than%20100%20jets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20May%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboeing-donald-trump-middle-east-qatar-air-force-one-747-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOrtberg%20accompanied%20Trump%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20a%20trip%20to%20Qatar%2C%20where%20Qatar%20Airways%20agreed%20to%20buy%20up%20to%20210%20Boeing%20jets%2C%20which%20the%20White%20House%20said%20was%20worth%20%2496%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Tuesday%20night's%20post%2C%20Trump%20said%20he%20would%20ask%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20to%20%26quot%3Bopen%20up%26quot%3B%20China%20so%20the%20business%20leaders%20%26quot%3Bcan%20work%20their%20magic%2C%20and%20help%20bring%20the%20People's%20Republic%20%5Bof%20China%5D%20to%20an%20even%20higher%20level!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-jensen-huang-air-force-one-trumps-trip-china-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778672904000%2C%2