r.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-using-ground-robots-most-promising-bombs-war-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eusing%20a%20fleet%20%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20ground%20robots%20to%20fight%20Russia's%20invasion%20while%20keeping%20its%20soldiers%20further%20back%20from%20the%20front%20lines.%20They're%20a%20newer%20but%20growing%20addition%20to%20its%20massive%20arsenal%20of%20uncrewed%20systems%20attacking%20and%20frustrating%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDevDroid%2C%20a%20Ukrainian%20robotic%20systems%20maker%2C%20said%20that%20pairing%20aerial%20drones%20with%20the%20ground%20robots%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-ground-robots-troops-uncrewed-ground-vehicles-first-quarter-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eunlocks%20even%20more%20options%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20capabilities%20in%20a%20fight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20an%20emerging%20form%20of%20robotic%20combined-arms%20warfare.%20Flying%20drones%20can%20scout%2C%20target%2C%20and%20guide%20the%20attack%2C%20while%20ground%20robots%20can%20bring%20heavier%20weapons%20and%20explosives%20directly%20to%20Russian%20positions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ground%20robots%20are%20very%20effective%20on%20their%20own%2C%20but%20%26quot%3Bwhen%20you%20use%20everything%20combined%2C%20it's%20more%20effective%20than%20using%20just%20an%20FPV%20drone%20or%20just%20a%20machine%20or%20just%20a%20ground%20drone%2C%26quot%3B%20Oleg%20Fedoryshyn%2C%20the%20director%20of%20R%26amp%3BD%20at%20DevDroid%2C%20told%20BI%2C%20referring%20to%20first-person-view%20drones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20green%20robots%20on%20wheels%20with%20guns%20mounted%20on%20them%20in%20a%20field%20of%20sunflowers%20under%20a%20blue%20sky%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a045e0495396a3b6e417d2f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUkraine%20is%20increasingly%20using%20ground%20robots%20for%20operations%20once%20done%20by%20soldiers%20or%20other%20weaponry.%3Cp%3EDiego%20Herrera%20Carcedo%2FAnadolu%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20different%20uncrewed%20systems%20have%20different%20strengths%20and%20weaknesses%20in%20battle.%20The%20robots%20can%20carry%20heavier%20weaponry%20and%20can%20often%20enter%20Russian%20positions%2C%20like%20dugouts%2C%20more%20easily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20aerial%20drones%20have%20the%20advantage%20in%20speed%20and%20overall%20situational%20awareness%3Cstrong%3E%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20something%20the%20robots%20hugging%20the%20ground%20lack.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flack-western-weapons-pushed-ukraine-make-gear-west-now-wants-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFlying%20drones%20can%20arrive%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20target%20positions%20first%20and%20inform%20other%20uncrewed%20operations%2C%20making%20the%20operation%20more%20effective%20overall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20in%20a%20combat%20situation%2C%20an%20aerial%20surveillance%20quadcopter%20drone%20%E2%80%94%20often%20cheaper%20and%20much%20more%20familiar%20to%20troops%20than%20robotic%20ground%20vehicles%20%E2%80%94%20can%20find%20targets%20and%20direct%20fire%20for%20a%20heavily%20armed%20robot%2C%20Fedoryshyn%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDevDroid%20makes%20a%20host%20of%20robotic%20systems%20as%20well%20as%20mounts%20so%20that%20weapons%2C%20like%20machine%20guns%20and%20grenade%20launchers%2C%20can%20be%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20weapons%20are%20heavy.%20The%20M2%20Browning%2C%20a%20century-old%20American%20machine%20gun%2C%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-m2-browning-gun-weapon-choice-ukraine-ai-fighting-robots-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epopular%20weapon%20for%20the%20robots%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20they%20are%20readily%20available%20in%20Ukraine%20and%20considered%20very%20reliable.%20It's%20considered%20too%20heavy%2C%20though%2C%20for%20one%20soldier%20to%20carry%20over%20long%20distances.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20quite%20hard%20for%20a%20soldier%20to%20take%20a%20Browning%20himself%2C%26quot%3B%20Fedoryshyn%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Ukrainian%20soldier%20in%20charge%20of%20his%20unit's%20ground%20robots%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20robots%20can%20also%20carry%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-ground-robots-hit-russia-more-explosives-flying-drones-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eheavy%20explosive%20payloads%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20pack%20much%20more%20of%20a%20punch%20than%20the%20explosive-laden%20FPV%20drones%20that%20are%20prolific%20along%20the%20front%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20crucial%20difference%20between%20aerial%20and%20on-the-ground%20unmanned%20systems%20is%20the%20mass%20that%20they%20can%20carry%2C%26quot%3B%20Oleksandr%20Yabchanka%2C%20the%20head%20of%20the%20robotic%20systems%20for%20Ukraine's%20Da%20Vinci%20Wolves%20Battalion%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20Ukraine%20needs%20to%20%26quot%3Balways%20be%20one%20step%2C%20half%20a%20step%20ahead%20of%20the%20enemy%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20powers%20of%20destruction.%26quot%3B%20And%20that's%20where%20the%20ground%20robots%20come%20into%20play.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20his%20unit%20drove%20a%20ground%20robot%20carrying%2066%20pounds%20of%20explosives%20into%20a%20basement%20held%20by%20Russia.%20The%20detonation%20eliminated%20the%20Russian%20infantry%20inside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYabchanka%20said%20that%20the%20biggest%20aerial%20drones%20can%20carry%20mines%20that%20weigh%2022%20pounds%20each%2C%20while%20the%20smallest%20ground%20robots%20that%20he%20works%20with%20can%20take%20more%20than%2048%20pounds.%20The%20larger%20ones%20can%20carry%20much%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225194%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20stands%20on%20a%20dirt%20road%20with%20a%20drone%20hovering%20above%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F695bcaa7832e0ef1ead7252d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223463%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDrones%20have%20become%20a%20vital%20weapon%20for%20Ukraine%2C%20but%20they%20have%20some%20limitations.%3Cp%3ESERGEY%20BOBOK%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20role%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-ground-robots-get-intel-russia-can-be-foiled-grass-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egathering%20intelligence%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20limited%20compared%20to%20drones%20in%20the%20sky%2C%20he%20said.%20His%20unit%20sometimes%20uses%20them%20that%20way%2C%20but%20the%20landscape%20makes%20it%20difficult.%20The%20robots'%20cameras%20can%20be%20easily%20blocked%20by%20tall%20grass%20and%20other%20vegetation.%20Putting%20eyes%20in%20the%20sky%20for%20these%20assets%20helps%20overcome%20that%20particular%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine's%20use%20of%20ground%20robots%20is%20soaring.%20Beyond%20attacks%20and%20reconnaissance%2C%20Ukraine%20is%20using%20them%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-veteran-west-must-copy-ukraine-keep-ground-robots-cheap-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eevacuate%20wounded%20soldiers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20lay%20and%20remove%20mines%2C%20and%20carry%20equipment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy%20said%20last%20month%20that%20Ukraine's%20ground%20robots%20had%20carried%20out%20more%20than%2022%2C000%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-using-ground-robots-most-promising-bombs-war-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emissions%20on%20the%20front%20lines%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20previous%20three%20months.%20He%20said%20they%20are%20replacing%20humans%20in%20risky%20actions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20marks%20a%20major%20increase%20from%20the%20around%202%2C000%20missions%20officials%20previously%20said%20ground%20robots%20had%20carried%20out%20in%20the%20six%20months%20leading%20up%20to%20December.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20is%20investing%20heavily%20in%20these%20systems.%20Zelenskyy%20said%20last%20month%20that%20he%20had%20tasked%20officials%20with%20making%20at%20least%2050%2C000%20ground%20robots%20this%20year%2C%20and%20Ukraine's%20defense%20minister%20said%20that%20the%20goal%20is%20to%20have%20100%25%20of%20front-line%20logistics%20done%20by%20robotic%20systems%20instead%20of%20humans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20wants%20robots%20to%20take%20over%20as%20many%20battlefield%20roles%20as%20possible%2C%20a%20priority%20for%20a%20country%20with%20a%20far%20smaller%20population%20and%20military%20than%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20Fedoryshyn%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20we%20will%20want%20to%20change%20all%20roles%20that%20we%20can%20change%20to%20save%20people's%20lives.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-drones-and-war-robots-working-together-are-more-effective-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778672449000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a03139eba7ef34b41f374ee%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-drones-and-war-robots-working-together-are-more-effective-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ukraine%20has%20a%20powerful%20and%20growing%20fleet%20of%20ground%20robots%20and%20flying%20drones%2C%20and%20using%20their%20different%20abilities%20together%20is%20unlocking%20new%20potential.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sbaker%40insider.com%20(Sin%C3%A9ad%20Baker)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A100%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I'm%20Wix's%20CMO.%20I%20use%20AI%20agents%20to%20survive%206%20a.m.%20meetings%2C%20and%20I'm%20rebuilding%20my%20team%20around%20'full-stack'%20marketers.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Omer%20Shai%20Wix%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a02e439c9dd4cb81cda96bc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221365%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOmer%20Shai%2C%20CMO%20of%20Wix%2C%20said%20he's%20reorienting%20his%20marketing%20department%20around%20%26quot%3Bfull-stack%20marketers%2C%26quot%3B%20thanks%20to%20AI.%3Cp%3EWix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EWix's%20CMO%20says%20he's%20deploying%20AI%20and%20%26quot%3Bsuper%20agents%26quot%3B%20to%20reshape%20his%20marketing%20department.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20version%20of%20this%20post%20appears%20in%20the%20CMO%20Insider%20newsletter.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EYou%20can%20sign%20up%20for%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsubscription%2Fnewsletter%2Fcmo-insider%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider's%20weekly%20marketing%20newsletter%20here%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Omer%20Shai%2C%20chief%20marketing%20officer%20of%20the%20website-building%20platform%20Wix.%20It's%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20department%20has%20been%20using%20AI%20for%20years%20in%20terms%20of%20thinking%20about%20creative%2C%20and%20using%20the%20tools%20to%20make%20our%20lives%20easier.%20I'm%20working%20with%20all%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ELLMs%20like%20ChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Gemini%2C%20and%20Claude.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20much%20easier%20for%20me%20to%20work%20with%20the%20team%20because%20I%20can%20be%20much%20clearer%20with%20what%20I%20would%20like%20to%20create.%20Even%20though%20I'm%20not%20a%20content%20writer%20or%20creative%20person%2C%20I%20know%20how%20to%20work%20with%20tools%20that%20can%20bring%20us%20to%2070%25%20or%2080%25%20of%20my%20idea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20working%20with%20my%20own%20super%20agent%20that%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvibe-coding-asana-productivity-tool-software-stocks-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecreated%20on%20Base44%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbase44-vibecoding-tools-easy-to-copy-maor-shlomo-risk-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecompany%20we%20bought%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20in%20Sydney%2C%20Australia%2C%20so%20I%20have%20very%20late%20meetings%20and%20very%20early%20mornings%20%E2%80%94%20things%20that%20are%20horrible%20in%20the%20UI%20of%20a%20calendar%20because%20you%20only%20see%20the%20day%20you%20are%20in.%20I%20have%20a%20meeting%20at%206%20a.m.%20most%20of%20my%20days%2C%20and%20I%20like%20to%20prepare.%20Once%20I%20woke%20at%205.40%20a.m.%2C%2010%20minutes%20before%20I%20got%20the%20alert%20that%20I%20had%20a%20meeting%2C%20it%20caught%20me%20by%20surprise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20set%20up%20my%20super%20agent%20so%20that%20the%20night%20before%20my%20meetings%2C%20it%20automatically%20sends%20me%20a%20reminder%20of%20what's%20on%20my%20calendar%20the%20next%20day%2C%20along%20with%20prep%20materials%20for%20each%20meeting.%20So%20I%20start%20every%20day%20already%20briefed%20and%20ready%20to%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20responsible%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvibe-coding-website-lovable-wix-ai-writing-portfolio-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBase44's%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20both%20a%20CRO%20and%20a%20CMO.%20My%20agent%20is%20connected%20to%20HubSpot%2C%20my%20email%2C%20and%20my%20calendar.%20It%20reviews%20all%20the%20leads%20we%20receive%20and%20sends%20alerts%20based%20on%20each%20lead's%20urgency%20and%20potential.%20I%20get%20daily%20reports%20of%20the%20health%20of%20the%20leads%20and%20where%20they%20are%20in%20the%20pipeline.%20I%20created%20this%20specific%20application%2C%20so%20I%20don't%20need%20to%20work%20with%20anyone.%20I%20can%20do%20everything%20by%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20have%20an%20application%20for%20social%20listening%20that%20measures%20any%20posts%20that%20are%20published%20online%20and%20on%20social%20platforms%2C%20and%20the%20engagement%20and%20traffic%20that%20they%20get.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20more%20of%20a%20WhatsApp%20person%2C%20so%20I%20have%20an%20agent%20that%20works%20with%20my%20Slack%20to%20help%20me%20get%20the%20information%20that's%20important%20to%20me%20that%20I%20might%20miss%20in%20the%20channels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20for%20me%20is%20like%20a%20superpower.%20I%20think%20that%20I'm%20much%20smarter%20today%20than%20I%20used%20to%20be%20because%20of%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20difficult%20to%20quantify%20the%20time%20savings%20in%20a%20straightforward%20way%2C%20and%20that's%20actually%20part%20of%20the%20point.%20It's%20not%20just%20that%20the%20agent%20is%20doing%20things%20faster.%20That's%20why%20I%20say%20it%20gives%20people%20superpowers%2C%20it%20expands%20what's%20possible%2C%20not%20just%20what's%20efficient.%20To%20put%20a%20number%20on%20it%20would%20actually%20undersell%20what%20it%20does.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22be0ad342-4d0d-4d6c-b474-97a65ac8a85a%5C%22%3EWix%20is%20reshaping%20its%20marketing%20department%20around%20'full-stack%20marketers'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20in%20the%20process%20of%20changing%20the%20job%20roles%20like%20%26quot%3Bcontent%20writer%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bproduct%20marketer%26quot%3B%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpublicis-sapient-cmo-ai-forcing-an-overdue-marketing-reckoning-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20marketing%20department%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I'm%20trying%20to%20create%20more%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bfull-stack%20marketer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20full-stack%20marketer%20can%20take%20projects%20from%20almost%20the%20beginning%20to%20the%20end.%20I%20will%20need%20to%20create%20a%20lot%20of%20systems%20to%20support%20them%2C%20like%20brand%20guidance%20and%20feedback.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20in%20the%20process%20of%20making%20the%20department%20much%20more%20shallow%20and%20moving%20much%20faster%20from%20idea%20to%20production.%20Take%20the%20designer%20example%3A%20this%20means%20the%20designer%20doesn't%20get%20stuck%20in%20a%20feedback%20loop%20waiting%20for%20a%20content%20writer%20to%20provide%20the%20text.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20just%20need%20smart%20people.%20You%20need%20curiosity%20and%20an%20open%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20much%20easier%20for%20the%20younger%20generation%20than%20people%20in%20their%2030s%20and%2040s%20because%20those%20are%20the%20people%20who%20need%20to%20adjust%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20time%2C%20we%20are%20the%20ones%20to%20put%20boundaries%20on%20what%20it%20means%20to%20be%20a%20designer%20or%20in%20product%20marketing.%20For%20example%2C%20my%20designers%20are%20creating%20content%2C%20and%20they%20are%20also%20responsible%20for%20the%20text.%20I%20started%20cutting%20those%20barriers%20years%20ago%2C%20and%20with%20the%20tools%2C%20it's%20much%2C%20much%20easier%20for%20me%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20combination%20of%20very%20talented%20people%20and%20powerful%20AI%20tools%20means%20that%20smart%20people%20are%20no%20longer%20limited%20to%20their%20defined%20lane.%20They%20can%20do%20more%2C%20so%20they%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwix-cmo-uses-ai-super-agents-full-stack-marketers-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778672401000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a02e448ba7ef34b41f3743f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwix-cmo-uses-ai-super-agents-full-stack-marketers-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Wix's%20CMO%20says%20he's%20deploying%20AI%20and%20%26quot%3Bsuper%20agents%26quot%3B%20to%20reshape%20his%20marketing%20department%2C%20and%20changing%20up%20roles.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22loreilly%40insider.com%20(Lara%20O'Reilly)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Can%20a%2015%25%20gold%20duty%20fix%20India's%20trade%20deficit%3F%20The%20math%20is%20not%20simple%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778672383000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2026-04%2F07%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F1200X628%2F1775546244-649.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fcan-a-15-pc-gold-duty-fix-indian-trade-deficit-math-explained-126051301140_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20may%20need%20a%20steep%20fall%20in%20gold%20imports%20to%20ease%20its%20trade%20deficit%2C%20but%20high%20prices%2C%20investment%20demand%20and%20smuggling%20risks%20complicate%20the%20duty%20hike's%20impact%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A100%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fcan-a-15-pc-gold-duty-fix-indian-trade-deficit-math-explained-126051301140_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fcan-a-15-pc-gold-duty-fix-indian-trade-deficit-math-explained-126051301140_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fcan-a-15-pc-gold-duty-fix-indian-trade-deficit-math-explained-126051301140_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gujarat%20Police%20Bans%20Public%20Shaming%2C%20Parading%20Of%20Accused%20In%20New%20Directive%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22The%20new%20guidelines%20mandate%20that%20police%20officers%20must%20ensure%20the%20self-respect%20and%20dignity%20of%20an%20accused%20person%20remains%20intact%20from%20the%20mome