20in%20the%20CMO%20Insider%20newsletter.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EYou%20can%20sign%20up%20for%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsubscription%2Fnewsletter%2Fcmo-insider%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider's%20weekly%20marketing%20newsletter%20here%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20do%20CMOs%20want%20from%20TV%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftv-ad-upfronts-week-takeaways-youtube-amazon-netflix-sports-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETV%20upfronts%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20happening%20this%20week%20in%20New%20York%20City%2C%20are%20largely%20a%20series%20of%20pitches%20to%20agency%20buyers%20by%20entertainment%20giants%20hoping%20to%20secure%20big%20spending%20commitments.%20But%20it's%20the%20marketers%20working%20at%20brands%20who%20actually%20control%20the%20ad%20budgets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spoke%20with%20top%20marketers%20about%20what%20they're%20focused%20on%20this%20year%2C%20as%20the%20industry%20descends%20on%20Manhattan's%20theaters%20and%20music%20halls%20for%20a%20parade%20of%20celebrity%20cameos%2C%20splashy%20trailers%2C%20and%20billion-dollar%20sales%20pitches.%20(One%20new%20entrant%20on%20the%20unofficial%20upfronts%20calendar%20this%20year%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmrbeast-jimmy-donaldson-pitching-advertisers-swanky-exclusive-event-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EYouTuber%20MrBeast%3C%2Fa%3E%20held%20an%20invite-only%20breakfast%20at%20the%20swanky%20Penthouse%2045%20event%20space%20to%20woo%20advertisers.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hot%20topics%3A%20measurement%2C%20live%20sports%2C%20and%20flexibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlyson%20Griffin%2C%20head%20of%20marketing%20at%20State%20Farm%2C%20told%20me%20that%20the%20aim%20of%20the%20upfront%20has%20evolved%20far%20beyond%20rate%20negotiations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20upfront%20feels%20like%20a%20turning%20point%20where%20transparency%2C%20performance%20accountability%2C%20and%20buyer-friendly%20execution%20are%20as%20important%20as%20pricing%2C%26quot%3B%20Griffin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECMOs%20are%20also%20all%20about%20sports%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20the%20last%20remaining%20mass-reach%20TV%20vehicles.%20And%2C%20in%20an%20uncertain%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-ceos-execs-say-about-impact-of-iran-war-business-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egeopolitical%20and%20macroeconomic%20environment%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20marketers%20are%20pressing%20networks%20to%20be%20flexible%20about%20how%20deals%20are%20structured.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20need%20to%20be%20thoughtful%20about%20locking%20in%20significant%20spend%20too%20early%2C%26quot%3B%20GEICO's%20VP%20of%20integrated%20marketing%20and%20media%2C%20Kate%20Jalkut%2C%20told%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20three%20of%20the%20biggest%20topics%20for%20marketers%20dominating%20the%202026%20TV%20upfronts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b27e8a8b-25e3-4e2a-90e2-aa3b116b80ed%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20How%20does%20TV%20impact%20my%20bottom%20line%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EState%20Farm%20isn't%20alone%20in%20looking%20for%20more%20ways%20to%20tie%20TV%20spending%20to%20business%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20than%2045%25%20of%20marketers%20said%20business%20outcomes%20are%20the%20most%20critical%20factor%20when%20deciding%20which%20media%20to%20buy%2C%20per%20a%20recent%20survey%20from%20the%20TV%20measurement%20company%20iSpot.%20Yet%2047%25%20of%20marketers%20polled%20said%20measuring%20outcomes%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%20challenge.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22seth%20meyers%20nbcu%20upfront%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a03674e58810e27922acc88%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESeth%20Meyers%20took%20to%20the%20stage%20for%20NBCUniversal's%202026%20upfront%20at%20Radio%20City%20Music%20Hall.%3Cp%3E%3A%20Ralph%20Bavaro%2FNBCUniversal%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20partly%20because%20there%20isn't%20a%20standard%20way%20to%20measure%20outcomes%20across%20the%20industry.%20There's%20consensus%20that%20it%20matters%20and%20should%20be%20a%20criterion%20going%20forward%2C%20but%20there's%20no%20agreement%20on%20the%20actual%20definition%2C%20said%20Vicky%20Chang%2C%20head%20of%20media%20investment%20at%20Tatari%2C%20a%20TV-buying%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMarketers%20are%20running%20out%20of%20patience%20for%20hand-wavy%20metrics%20that%20gesture%20toward%20outcomes%20without%20actually%20delivering%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Chang%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETV%20networks%20are%20aware%20of%20the%20problem%20and%20have%20presented%20a%20partial%20solution.%20On%20Wednesday%2C%20OpenAP%2C%20an%20adtech%20company%20jointly%20owned%20by%20some%20of%20the%20biggest%20US%20TV%20networks%2C%20made%20a%20big%20outcomes-based%20play.%20It's%20launching%20a%20standard%20to%20connect%20data%20from%20TV%20companies%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0about%20who%20saw%20a%20campaign%20%E2%80%94%20with%20data%20from%20advertisers%20about%20which%20users%20performed%20an%20action%2C%20such%20as%20visiting%20a%20website%20or%20buying%20a%20product.%20The%20major%20TV%20networks%20are%20on%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdvertisers%20have%20long-standing%20gripes%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-advertising-tv-networks-nielsen-ddb-omnicom-dreamlines-cruises-2021-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETV%20measurement%20methodologies%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20ad%20loads%20on%20streaming%20TV.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBrands%20need%20holistic%20visibility%20into%20exposure%20and%20incremental%20reach%20across%20platforms%20to%20reduce%20duplication%20and%20maximize%20efficiency%2C%26quot%3B%20State%20Farm's%20Griffin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20that%20networks%20and%20streamers%20need%20to%20offer%20measurement%20that%20captures%20metrics%20like%20attention%2C%20engagement%2C%20and%20business%20impact%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20impressions%20or%20GRPs%2C%20the%20old-school%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffacebook-introduces-gross-rating-points-for-video-ad-buying-2015-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egross%20ratings%20points%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20metric%20beloved%20by%20TV%20planners%20since%20the%20'50s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ac8a57d0-0950-4a1a-bd32-c1f8c16f199e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Marketers%20can't%20get%20enough%20of%20sports%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20premium%20TV%20programming%2C%20sports%20dominate%2C%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnfl-dominates-broadcast-tv-ratings-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENFL%20at%20the%20top%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENFL%20legends%20Tom%20Brady%20and%20Rob%20Gronkowski%20were%20onstage%20at%20the%20Fox%20upfront%2C%20where%20the%20network%20showed%20off%20its%20forthcoming%20football%20lineup%20and%20a%20new%20weekly%20soccer%20show.%20Sportscaster%20Charissa%20Thompson%20joined%20Andrew%20Whitworth%2C%20Ryan%20Fitzpatrick%2C%20and%20Matthew%20Stafford%20at%20Amazon's%20upfront%2C%20where%20it%20touted%20%26quot%3BThursday%20Night%20Football%26quot%3B%20as%20its%20big%20draw.%20Over%20at%20NBCUniversal%2C%20it%20was%20all%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.adweek.com%2Fconvergent-tv%2Fnbcu-upfront-week-kickoff-sports-ai-and-vin-diesel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESunday%20night%20sports%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20from%20football%20to%20basketball%20and%20baseball.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjimmy-kimmel-makes-fun-trump-beef-bachelorette-disney-ad-presentation-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDisney%20pitched%20hard%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20Super%20Bowl%20and%20ESPN's%20plans%20to%20turn%20Santa%20Monica%20Beach%20into%20%26quot%3BESPN%20Beach%26quot%3B%20for%20big%20game%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227362%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Amazon%20football%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a03687958810e27922acc8d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224908%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMarketers%20are%20looking%20to%20extend%20their%20football%20ad%20buys%20into%20the%20pre-%20and%20post-game%20and%20social%20media%20integrations.%3Cp%3ECooper%20Neill%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20so%20few%20opportunities%20for%20watercooler%20TV%20moments%20anymore%20outside%20sports%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Eric%20Haggstrom%2C%20an%20SVP%20at%20the%20research%20firm%20Advertiser%20Perceptions%2C%20which%20regularly%20polls%20CMOs%20and%20media%20buyers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarketers%20this%20year%20want%20to%20know%20how%20they%20can%20maximize%20their%20sports%20budgets%20outside%2030-second%20commercials%20in%20live%20broadcasts.%20That%20includes%20integrations%20in%20the%20pre-%20and%20post-game%2C%20and%20partnering%20with%20athletes%20for%20social%20content%2C%20Haggstrom%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20need%20solutions%20that%20go%20beyond%20in-game%20logo%20presence%2C%26quot%3B%20GEICO's%20Jalkut%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJalkut%20is%20keeping%20an%20eye%20out%20for%20more%20dynamic%20ad%20insertion%20products%2C%20interactive%20formats%2C%20sharper%20audience%20segmentation%2C%20clearer%20ways%20to%20separate%20competitors%20in%20cluttered%20categories%20during%20ad%20breaks%2C%20and%20more%20%26quot%3Bsecond-screen%20synchronization%26quot%3B%20that%20lets%20broadcasters%20expand%20their%20content%20%E2%80%94%20including%20ads%20and%20sponsorships%20%E2%80%94%20beyond%20the%20TV%20set.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225323cf93-8ed7-4da6-8a21-0e397e07dff9%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Flexibility%20is%20key%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECMOs%20are%20heading%20to%20the%20upfronts%20unc