C%20and%20deep-sea%20warfare%20will%20play%20a%20big%20role.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpalmer-luckey-america-worlds-gun-store-defense-tech-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAnduril%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20raised%20%245%20billion%20and%20doubled%20its%20value%20to%20%2461%20billion%2C%20the%20defense%20tech%20company%20said%20on%20Wednesday.%20Its%20CEO%20shared%20some%20thoughts%20on%20the%20future%20of%20warfare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFounded%20in%202017%20by%20Palmer%20Luckey%20and%20four%20cofounders%2C%20Anduril's%20mission%20is%20to%20modernize%20the%20US%20military%20and%20develop%20autonomous%20weapons%20that%20it%20says%20%26quot%3Bwill%20save%20Western%20civilization.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20valued%20at%20just%20over%20%2430%20billion%20in%20June%202025.%20The%20company%2C%20which%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanduril-palmer-luckey-us-air-force-contract-defense-tech-startup-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esecured%20Pentagon%20contracts%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20is%20considered%20an%20IPO%20candidate%20in%20the%20not-too-distant%20future.%20Its%20latest%20funding%20round%20was%20led%20by%20Thrive%20Capital%20and%20Andreessen%20Horowitz.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlongside%20the%20funding%20announcement%2C%20Brian%20Schimpf%2C%20Anduril's%20CEO%2C%20shared%20the%20letter%20he%20sent%20to%20investors%20in%20January%2C%20laying%20out%20how%20Anduril%20believes%20the%20nature%20of%20conflict%20will%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20publishing%20the%20letter%20publicly%20because%20these%20issues%20extend%20well%20beyond%20any%20one%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20Schimpf%20said.%20Here%20are%20four%20of%20his%20predictions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a820ba22-3808-43b2-b702-9fe2e9a7b6dd%5C%22%3E1.%20The%20future%20of%20war%20is%20software-heavy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESchimpf%20said%20AI%20and%20autonomy%20are%20changing%20the%20meaning%20of%20military%20scale%2C%20with%20future%20conflicts%20favoring%20forces%20that%20can%20coordinate%20large%20numbers%20of%20connected%2C%20software-enabled%20systems%20rather%20than%20rely%20only%20on%20the%20most%20expensive%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20central%20to%20Anduril's%20pitch.%20The%20company's%20autonomous%20drones%20and%20vehicles%20are%20underpinned%20by%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanduril-palmer-luckey-ai-war-conflict-defense-tech-startups-military-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esoftware%20platform%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Lattice%20OS%2C%20a%20digital%20command-and-control%20center%20that%20uses%20AI%20to%20integrate%20data%20from%20drones%2C%20cameras%2C%20sensors%2C%20and%20radar%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFuture%20conflicts%20will%20be%20decided%20by%20the%20ability%20to%20generate%20targeting%20faster%2C%20deliver%20effects%20at%20range%20in%20volume%2C%20and%20deny%20the%20same%20to%20our%20adversaries%2C%26quot%3B%20Schimpf%20told%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20requires%20a%20%26quot%3Bdistributed%2C%20software-defined%20system%20for%20sensing%2C%20targeting%2C%20and%20strike%2C%26quot%3B%20that%20can%20be%20continuously%20updated%20rather%20than%20%26quot%3Blocked%20into%20configurations%20for%20thirty-year%20service%20lives.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20software%20will%20be%20central%20to%20how%20militaries%20find%20targets%2C%20coordinate%20weapons%2C%20survive%20attacks%2C%20and%20adapt%20in%20real%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228e9948c6-e68b-43f4-831c-899f74877953%5C%22%3E2.%20Hiding%20will%20be%20harder%2C%20making%20the%20deep%20sea%20more%20important%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESchimpf%20said%20autonomous%20advances%20in%20sensing%20will%20make%20it%20%26quot%3Bnearly%20impossible%26quot%3B%20for%20militaries%20to%20conceal%20activity%20across%20air%2C%20ground%2C%20and%20surface%20domains.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20shift%20will%20make%20the%20deep-sea%20a%20rare%20domain%20where%20sensing%20remains%20difficult%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20underwater%20operations%20would%20become%20%26quot%3Bdisproportionately%20important.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbove%20ground%2C%20militaries%20will%20need%20to%20improve%20mass%20(the%20concentration%20of%20combat%20power)%2C%20dispersion%2C%20and%20resilience%20to%20survive%20in%20environments%20where%20they%20are%20more%20easily%20detected%20and%20targeted%2C%20said%20Schimpf.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22454f45f5-6cae-4de9-b7a8-ceadee8fd9ba%5C%22%3E3.%20Alliance%20structures%20are%20going%20to%20shift%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESchimpf%20told%20investors%20that%20the%20world%20had%20entered%20a%20new%20Cold%20War%20period%2C%20writing%20that%20future%20conflicts%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bregional%20and%20bifurcated.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20in%20the%20first%20Cold%20War%2C%20the%20U.S.-China%20relationship%20will%20likely%20proceed%20through%20a%20framework%20of%20containment%20and%20managed%20competition%20in%20which%20both%20sides%20maintain%20common%20rules%20while%20avoiding%20open%20conflict%2C%26quot%3B%20Schimpf%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChina's%20military%20buildup%20and%20the%20US%20prioritizing%20hemispheric%20defense%20will%20force%20allies%20to%20take%20more%20responsibility%20for%20regional%20deterrence%2C%20and%20alliance%20structures%20will%20shift%2C%20said%20Schimpf.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20pointed%20to%20multiple%20defense%20assessments%20that%20predict%202027%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20window%20of%20maximum%20danger%20with%20China%2C%26quot%3B%20when%20Beijing%20may%20assess%20it%20has%20sufficient%20capability%20and%20opportunity%20to%20act.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2232187cd2-bfdc-49fd-b747-83f6764b9049%5C%22%3E4.%20Future%20conflicts%20will%20be%20won%20by%20the%20ability%20to%20produce%20at%20scale%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDeterrence%20will%20depend%20on%20how%20quickly%20countries%20can%20rebuild%20combat%20power%20and%20turn%20technological%20advances%20into%20military%20capability%20at%20scale%2C%20said%20Schimpf.%20%26quot%3BThe%20side%20that%20adapts%20fastest%20shapes%20the%20terms%20of%20competition%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20doesn't%20mean%20mass-producing%20poor-quality%20weaponry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20Schimpf%20said%20future%20conflicts%20will%20require%20%26quot%3Bintelligent%20mass%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20he%20described%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20mix%20of%20high-end%20and%20scalable%20systems%20that%20combine%20precision%20with%20producibility.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIntelligent%2C%20networked%20mass%20will%20replace%20the%20industrial-age%20attrition%20of%20previous%20centuries%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20meet%20that%20demand%2C%20the%20production%20timeline%20for%20lower-end%20capabilities%20must%20shrink%20from%20decades%20to%20months%20or%20years%2C%20Schimpf%20wrote%2C%20arguing%20that%20the%20traditional%20defense-industrial%20model%20%E2%80%94%20built%20around%20low-rate%20production%20of%20exquisite%20platforms%20over%20decades%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3Bdoes%20not%20make%20sense%20today.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanduril-ceo-brian-schimpf-future-war-funding-valuation-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778671408000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a04347a95396a3b6e417caf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanduril-ceo-brian-schimpf-future-war-funding-valuation-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Anduril%20CEO%20Brian%20Schimpf%20published%20his%20letter%20to%20investors%20outlining%20how%20conflict%20will%20change%2C%20including%20a%20focus%20on%20deep-sea%20warfare.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22pthompson%40businessinsider.com%20(Polly%20Thompson)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mik