nitial%20post-mortem%20report%2C%20the%20sources%20added.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprateek-yadav-death-no-marks-on-prateek-yadavs-body-blue-tint-on-toes-due-to-disease-sources-11489331%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprateek-yadav-death-no-marks-on-prateek-yadavs-body-blue-tint-on-toes-due-to-disease-sources-11489331%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprateek-yadav-death-no-marks-on-prateek-yadavs-body-blue-tint-on-toes-due-to-disease-sources-11489331%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Anthropic's%20Claude%20is%20telling%20users%20to%20'go%20to%20bed'%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20internet%20has%20theories%20why%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Anthropic%20Claude%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a04497195396a3b6e417cf9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAnthropic's%20Claude%20has%20been%20giving%20some%20unusual%20advice%20to%20users.%3Cp%3EBloomberg%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAnthropic's%20Claude%20AI%20has%20been%20telling%20users%20to%20get%20some%20rest.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EClaude%20users%20have%20been%20speculating%20over%20what's%20causing%20it.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt's%20the%20latest%20example%20of%20AI%20exhibiting%20quirky%20behavior%20after%20ChatGPT's%20%26quot%3BGoblin%20Mode.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIs%20Claude%20telling%20you%20to%20%26quot%3Bgo%20to%20bed%26quot%3B%3F%20You're%20not%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20few%20months%2C%20scores%20of%20people%20using%20Anthropic's%20Claude%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2FClaudeAI%2Fcomments%2F1ruryxo%2Fclaude_decided_i_need_a_bedtime_apparently%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eposted%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20social%20media%20that%20the%20AI%20chatbot%20is%20telling%20them%20to%20%26quot%3Bget%20some%20sleep%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bgo%20rest%26quot%3B%20after%20long%20sessions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENobody%20seems%20to%20know%20why%2C%20but%20many%20have%20theories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20idea%20put%20forward%20is%20that%20Anthropic%20has%20trained%20Claude%20to%20look%20after%20user%20well-being%20and%20discourage%20unhealthy%20attachments%20to%20the%20chatbot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20likened%20it%20to%20a%20nagging%20parent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BClaude's%20emphasis%20on%20bedtime%20reminds%20me%20of%20my%20parents%20when%20I%20showed%20irritability%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20one%20Reddit%20user%20in%20a%20February%20discussion%20about%20Claude's%20behavior.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPerhaps%20its%20training%20data%20works%20on%20an%20old-fashioned%20folk%20solution%20to%20childhood%20irritation%20and%20parental%20fatigue.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESam%20McAllister%2C%20a%20member%20of%20staff%20at%20Anthropic%2C%20said%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fsammcallister%2Fstatus%2F2053916962477215771%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EX%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20week%20that%20the%20behavior%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bbit%20of%20a%20character%20tic%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20the%20company%20is%20%26quot%3Baware%20of%20this%20and%20hoping%20to%20fix%20it%20in%20future%20models.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20users%20suggested%20that%20Claude%20was%20basing%20its%20reminders%20on%20the%20local%20timestamp%20of%20when%20the%20chat%20was%20started.%20McAllister%20said%20that%20this%20is%20%26quot%3Boften%20wrong%26quot%3B%20because%20it%20tells%20him%20to%20go%20to%20sleep%20during%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVery%20useful%20when%20right%20though.%20Just%20too%20'coddling'%20at%20times%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20theory%20is%20more%20cynical%3A%20Claude%20is%20nudging%20users%20to%20end%20chats%20to%20save%20its%20computing%20resources.%20Anthropic's%20Claude%20models%20have%20experienced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fis-claude-down-outage-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emultiple%20outages%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20year%20as%20their%20popularity%20soared%2C%20particularly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclaude-outages-anthropic-ai-software-engineers-developers-coding-dependance-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eamong%20software%20developers%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20Anthropic%20signed%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-deal-to-use-elon-musks-colossus-data-center%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edeal%20with%20Elon%20Musk's%20SpaceX%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20more%20computing%20capacity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnthropic%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClaude's%20%26quot%3Bgo%20to%20bed%26quot%3B%20messages%20are%20the%20latest%20example%20of%20quirky%20behavior%20from%20AI.%20Earlier%20this%20year%2C%20ChatGPT%20had%20a%20habit%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-really-really-wants-gpt55-stop-talking-about-goblins-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etalking%20about%20goblins%3C%2Fa%3E%20until%20OpenAI%20added%20instructions%20to%20its%20source%20code%20to%20stop.%20OpenAI%20said%20it%20stemmed%20from%20a%20%26quot%3BNerdy%26quot%3B%20personality%20option%20for%20ChatGPT%20and%20that%20it%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bpowerful%20example%20of%20how%20reward%20signals%20can%20shape%20model%20behavior%20in%20unexpected%20ways.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERegardless%20of%20why%20it's%20telling%20people%20to%20go%20to%20bed%2C%20Claude%20is%20probably%20right%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-get-better-sleep-millionaire-advice-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emost%20of%20us%20likely%20do%20need%20more%20sleep.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-claude-go-to-bed-why-users-sleep-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778670766000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a044fb87c7e83f26041b215%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-claude-go-to-bed-why-users-sleep-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Anthropic's%20Claude%20AI%20has%20been%20taking%20on%20the%20role%20of%20a%20nagging%20parent%2C%20and%20users%20are%20wondering%20what's%20behind%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22rscammell%40businessinsider.com%20(Robert%20Scammell)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'EPS%20has%20no%20such%20idea'%3A%20Rebel%20AIADMK%20MLA%20lobs%20'betrayer'%20charge%20at%20party%20chief%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778670506000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-131063800%2Cimgsize-819901.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Feps-has-no-such-idea-rebel-aiadmk-mla-shanmugam-turns-betrayer-charge-on-party-chief%2Farticleshow%2F131062887.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22AIADMK%20faces%20a%20severe%20internal%20crisis%20as%20a%20faction%20of%20MLAs%2C%20led%20by%20C.V.%20Shanmugam%2C%20openly%20rebelled%20against%20party%20chief%20Edappadi%20Palaniswami.%20They%20allege%20EPS%20explored%20aligning%20with%20the%20DMK%20and%20abandoned%20the%20party's%20core%20anti-DMK%20stance.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Air%20India%20cuts%20120%20weekly%20international%20flights%20amid%20West%20Asia%20conflict%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778670471000%2C%22vi