ing%20on%20quarterly%20results%2C%20stressing%20that%20patience%20and%20quality%20build%20lasting%20brand%20value.%20This%20approach%20fosters%20trust%20and%20customer%20loyalty%2C%20crucial%20for%20enduring%20appeal.%20Companies%20prioritizing%20short-term%20gains%20risk%20damaging%20their%20reputation%20and%20future.%20Arnault's%20philosophy%20offers%20a%20sustainable%20path%20to%20outperforming%20peers%20financially.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fbernard-arnaults-simple-billionaire-business-lesson-that-most-companies-forget-under-pressure%2Farticleshow%2F131034994.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fbernard-arnaults-simple-billionaire-business-lesson-that-most-companies-forget-under-pressure%2Famp_articleshow%2F131034994.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fbernard-arnaults-simple-billionaire-business-lesson-that-most-companies-forget-under-pressure%2Famp_articleshow%2F131034994.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I'm%20a%20mom%20of%203%20kids%2C%20and%20I%20took%20a%20quick%20getaway%20to%20help%20me%20prepare%20for%20a%20busy%20summer.%20It%20was%20just%20what%20I%20needed.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221940%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rebecca%20Hastings%20and%20her%20husband%20in%20front%20of%20their%20cabin%20at%20Hinata%20Retreat.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a01dec8ba7ef34b41f36f5f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221455%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20and%20her%20husband%20went%20to%20Hinata%20Retreat%20in%20Massachusetts%20for%20a%20getaway%20before%20a%20busy%20summer.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Rebecca%20Hastings%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20have%20three%20kids%2C%20and%20summer%20can%20be%20busy.%20My%20calendar%20for%20the%20coming%20season%20is%20already%20booked.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBefore%20things%20get%20too%20hectic%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20book%20a%20quick%20trip%20for%20my%20husband%20and%20me%20to%20reset.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20was%20hard%20to%20completely%20unplug%2C%20but%20it%20was%20still%20just%20what%20I%20needed.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20May%20hit%2C%20every%20weekend%20on%20my%20calendar%20was%20already%20booked%20%E2%80%94%20and%20summer%20hadn't%20even%20started.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESomewhere%20between%20having%20babies%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparents-say-teens-tough-love-raising-high-school-kids-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eraising%20three%20teenagers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20season%20that's%20supposed%20to%20feel%20relaxed%20had%20become%20one%20of%20the%20most%20exhausting%20times%20of%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20knew%20going%20into%20a%20busy%20season%20with%20little%20reserve%20in%20my%20tank%20wasn't%20going%20to%20be%20good%20for%20anyone.%20Before%20I%20could%20overthink%20it%2C%20I%20booked%20a%20short%20getaway.%20I%20needed%20a%20few%20days%20to%20regroup%2C%20and%20I%20couldn't%20do%20that%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223b1556db-ebb4-43a2-ab42-d560bc036935%5C%22%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20took%20a%20quick%2C%20much-needed%20getaway%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20booked%20a%20stay%20for%20my%20husband%20and%20me%20at%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbi-today-why-you-need-an-adults-only-vacation-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadults-only%20luxury%20getaway%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Massachusetts.%20Not%20an%20action-packed%20vacation%20or%20a%20sightseeing%20adventure%20%E2%80%94%20just%20space%20to%20decompress.%20As%20I%20clicked%20confirm%2C%20I%20hoped%20it%20would%20help%20me%20look%20forward%20to%20the%20months%20ahead%20as%20much%20as%20my%20kids%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20getaway%20started%20as%20soon%20as%20we%20drove%20out%20of%20our%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmbracing%20the%20purpose%20of%20the%20getaway%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20stopped%20at%20a%20favorite%20coffee%20shop%20for%20breakfast%20to%20launch%20our%20adventure.%20I%20ate%20a%20whole%20meal%20without%20anyone%20needing%20me.%20This%20was%20looking%20promising.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20few%20hours%20in%20the%20car%2C%20we%20arrived.%20The%20only%20thing%20I%20had%20planned%20was%20the%20location%20and%20a%20dinner%20reservation%20at%20the%20on-site%20restaurant.%20I%20resisted%20my%20typical%20approach%20to%20family%20travel%20of%20planning%20all%20the%20details%2C%20with%20backup%20plans%20just%20in%20case.%20There%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftraveled-to-over-40-countries-best-experiences-without-itinerary-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eno%20itinerary%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20this%20trip.%20Just%20time%20to%20exist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20felt%20foreign%2C%20but%20as%20soon%20as%20I%20entered%20the%20cabin%2C%20I%20exhaled%2C%20and%20my%20shoulders%20relaxed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20cabin%20at%20Hinata%20Retreat%20with%20views%20of%20a%20mountain%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a01dd9cc9dd4cb81cda91ca%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20cabin%20that%20the%20author%20and%20her%20husband%20stayed%20in%20at%20Hinata%20Retreat%20had%20gorgeous%20views.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Rebecca%20Hastings%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2217ede409-cf57-41c4-bbf3-c1193f1404ee%5C%22%3EBeing%20in%20a%20peaceful%20setting%20helped%20me%20relax%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFacing%20a%20wall%20of%20windows%20framing%20the%20Berkshire%20Mountains%2C%20no%20one%20was%20calling%2C%20%26quot%3BMom%2C%20look%20at%20this!%26quot%3B%20I%20could%20look%20out%20the%20windows%20and%20take%20in%20the%20beauty.%20Since%20we%20needed%20to%20stretch%20after%20the%20car%20ride%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20try%20one%20of%20the%20hiking%20trails%20on%20the%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20thing%20I%20noticed%20was%20how%20quiet%20it%20felt.%20There%20were%20no%20cars%2C%20nobody%20was%20talking%2C%20and%20no%20one%20needed%20me.%20I%20looked%20up%20at%20the%20trees%2C%20listened%20to%20the%20stream%2C%20and%20stopped%20to%20wonder%20at%20the%20fiddleheads%20growing%20along%20the%20path.%20Could%20I%20have%20done%20these%20things%20at%20home%3F%20Maybe.%20But%20I%20would%20have%20been%20thinking%20about%20what%20I%20needed%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feasy-dinners-under-30-minutes-meal-planning-recipes-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emake%20for%20dinner%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20who%20needed%20a%20ride%20to%20practice.%20Here%2C%20I%20let%20myself%20enjoy%20the%20forest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20and%20her%20husband%20at%20their%20getaway%20sitting%20on%20a%20couch.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a01ddedba7ef34b41f36f59%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThey%20enjoyed%20relaxing%20in%20the%20evening%20before%20a%20nice%20dinner.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Rebecca%20Hastings%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20returning%20to%20the%20cabin%20to%20get%20ready%20for%20dinner%2C%20we%20made%20our%20way%20to%20the%20restaurant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20stepped%20into%20the%20restaurant%2C%20I%20felt%20another%20exhale.%20Nothing%20felt%20rushed.%20I%20didn't%20need%20to%20hurry%20to%20choose%20a%20meal%20to%20keep%20the%20peace%20at%20the%20table.%20The%20staff%20suggested%20a%20few%20dishes%2C%20and%20for%20once%2C%20I%20didn't%20overthink%20it.%20I%20was%20happy%20to%20let%20someone%20else%20guide%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20appetizers%20came%2C%20my%20husband's%20phone%20buzzed.%20Our%20son%20was%20FaceTiming%20him%20from%20college.%20As%20my%20husband%20stepped%20outside%20to%20take%20the%20call%2C%20I%20resisted%20the%20urge%20to%20try%20to%20fix%20whatever%20was%20going%20on.%20I%20simply%20enjoyed%20a%20few%20bites%20of%20food.%20I%20couldn't%20remember%20the%20last%20time%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworld-happiness-report-more-people-eating-meals-alone-solo-dining-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eate%20alone%20in%20a%20restaurant%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20returned%20with%20a%20funny%20story%20of%20providing%20car%20help%20to%20my%20son%20via%20FaceTime.%20Leaving%20teens%20(even%20college%20ones)%20always%20makes%20me%20feel%20like%20I'm%20on%20the%20edge%20of%20my%20seat%2C%20ready%20for%20anything%20that%20might%20pop%20up.%20I%20did%20a%20quick%20check%20to%20make%20sure%20my%20youngest%20made%20it%20to%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fweekly-family-dinners-grandparents-house-tradition-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrandparents'%20house%3C%2Fa%3E%20before%20putting%20the%20phone%20aside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20private%20cabin%20the%20author%20stayed%20in%20at%20Hinata%20Retreat%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a01de34e1443b8dc48e3cf5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20cabin%20had%20a%20large%20soaking%20tub%2C%20a%20balcony%2C%20and%20a%20private%20hot%20tub.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Rebecca%20Hastings%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b9ac8e61-0790-4cbc-bbac-e073fcda2883%5C%22%3EAs%20a%20parent%2C%20it's%20hard%20to%20completely%20unplug%2C%20but%20I%20still%20enjoyed%20my%20trip%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20may%20have%20been%20away%20from%20home%2C%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrew-up-with-early-social-media-still-learning-to-unplug-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompletely%20unplugging%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20harder%20than%20I%20expected.%20Instead%20of%20setting%20hard%20rules%20about%20phones%20or%20checking%20on%20the%20kids%2C%20I%20just%20let%20things%20happen%20naturally.%20Too%20much%20pressure%20to%20make%20this%20getaway%20perfect%20would%20ruin%20the%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20enjoyed%20our%20meal%2C%20catching%20up%20on%20little%20things%20we%20miss%20during%20a%20busy%20week.%20We%20chatted%20about%20the%20view%20and%20shared%20two%20desserts.%20I%20found%20myself%20thinking%20about%20more%20trips%20we%20could%20take%2C%20how%20it%20felt%20so%20good%20to%20have%20a%20break%2C%20and%20how%20I%20needed%20this%20more%20than%20I%20realized.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rest%20of%20the%20evening%20was%20a%20blank%20slate%2C%20and%20I%20kept%20it%20that%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20in%20the%20cabin%2C%20I%20let%20myself%20simply%20exist.%20I%20sat%20in%20our%20private%20hot%20tub%20on%20the%20deck%2C%20the%20fire%20pit%20flickering%20next%20to%20me%20as%20I%20stared%20at%20the%20full%20moon.%20For%20the%20first%20time%20in%20a%20long%20time%2C%20I%20didn't%20need%20to%20plan%2C%20figure%20things%20out%2C%20or%20arrange%20anything.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20time%20I%20started%20thinking%20about%20home%2C%20the%20calm%20of%20the%20cabin%20pulled%20me%20back.%20The%20quiet%2C%20the%20view%2C%20the%20space%20to%20do%20nothing%2C%20it%20was%20filling%20a%20place%20in%20me%20I%20hadn't%20realized%20was%20empty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20didn't%20make%20sense%20to%20step%20away%20right%20before%20the%20busiest%20season%20of%20the%20year.%20But%20that's%20exactly%20why%20I%20needed%20to.%20Taking%20a%20few%20days%20to%20reset%20didn't%20take%20away%20from%20our%20summer%20%E2%80%94%20it%20helped%20me%20look%20forward%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-quick-trip-relax-before-busy-summer-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A17786701810