28000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20data%20center%20in%20Vernon%2C%20CA%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0378d47c7e83f26041ae36%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20data%20center%20in%20Vernon%2C%20CA%3Cp%3EMario%20Tama%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EPrivate%20credit's%20share%20of%20institutional%20portfolios%20has%20fallen%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECanoe%20Intelligence%20found%20that%20only%20infrastructure%20had%20net%20inflows%20from%20institutions%20in%20Q4%202025.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHedge%20funds%20and%20venture%20capital%20also%20gained%20a%20share%20of%20institutional%20investors'%20portfolios.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwall-street-private-credit-careers-asset-management-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPrivate%20credit%2C%20just%20recently%20one%20of%20the%20hottest%20asset%20classes%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20institutional%20investors%20to%20park%20their%20money%2C%20is%20losing%20ground%20to%20other%20strategies%2C%20according%20to%20a%20new%20report%20from%20Canoe%20Intelligence.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EPrivate%20credit%20accounted%20for%206.8%25%20of%20institutional%20investors'%20alternative-asset%20holdings%20in%20the%20fourth%20quarter%20of%202025%2C%20down%20from%209.7%25%20December%202024.%20However%2C%20the%20asset%20class's%20net%20asset%20value%20increased%20roughly%2020%25%20from%20June%202024%2C%20according%20to%20Canoe.%20The%20decline%20reflects%20a%20shift%20in%20portfolio%20composition%20as%20other%20assets%20grew%20faster%2C%20rather%20than%20a%20contraction%20in%20private%20credit%20assets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%2C%20sourced%20from%20primary%20documents%20across%2044%2C000%20funds%20that%20provide%20visibility%20into%20%2411%20trillion%20in%20AUM%2C%20tracks%20institutions%20giving%20money%20to%20and%20receiving%20money%20back%20from%20all%20sorts%20of%20alternative%20investors%2C%20from%20venture%20capital%20to%20hedge%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrivate%20credit's%20share%20of%20institutional%20portfolios%20has%20shrunk%20in%20part%20because%20investors%20have%20been%20receiving%20repayments%20and%20distributions%20from%20loans%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20asset%20class%20doing%20exactly%20what%20it%20is%20supposed%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mike%20Muniz%2C%20chief%20strategy%20officer%20at%20Canoe%20Intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20happens%20next%20is%20%26quot%3Bthe%20more%20consequential%20question%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20as%20new%20checks%20to%20private%20credit%20are%20not%20keeping%20pace%20with%20distributions%2C%20a%20sign%20that%20%26quot%3BLPs%20are%20not%20in%20a%20rush%20to%20redeploy%20at%20the%20same%20rate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20recently%20found%20that%20some%20institutions%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-credit-blue-owl-institutional-investors-redemptions-bdc-funding-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereducing%20or%20reassessing%20their%20investments%20in%20private%20credit%20retail%20funds%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20those%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblackstone-private-credit-warning-signs-financial-crisis-risks-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eretail-focused%20funds%20face%20record%20redemptions%3C%2Fa%3E%20amid%20concerns%20about%20private%20credit%20performance%20and%20the%20potential%20impact%20of%20AI.%20While%20retail%20investors%20are%20asking%20for%20their%20money%20back%2C%20institutional%20investors%20are%20choosing%20to%20put%20their%20gains%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20not%20the%20same%20as%20abandoning%20the%20asset%20class%2C%20but%20it%20does%20suggest%20a%20degree%20of%20selectivity%2C%26quot%3B%20Muniz%20said%20about%20the%20firm's%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFuture%20data%20on%20where%20investors%20are%20putting%20their%20money%20will%20help%20show%20whether%20this%20is%20a%20decision%20based%20on%20the%20spreads%20offered%20by%20private%20credit%20or%20%26quot%3Bmore%20attractive%20opportunities%20elsewhere%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%26quot%3BRight%20now%2C%20it%20points%20to%20patience%20rather%20than%20conviction%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221046%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Canoe%20Intelligence's%20chart%20on%20institutional%20allocation%20over%20time.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a039b6f7c7e83f26041b0b2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22672%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20chart%20showing%20the%20percent%20of%20institutional%20allocations%20over%20time.%3Cp%3ECanoe%20Intelligence%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20shows%20an%20increasing%20preference%20for%20the%20industry's%20largest%20players.%20The%2050%20biggest%20managers%20by%20AUM%2C%20who%20accounted%20for%2051%25%20of%20investors'%20net%20value%20in%20the%20fourth%20quarter%20of%20last%20year%2C%20up%206%25%20in%20one%20quarter%20after%20new%20capital%20commitments%20nearly%20doubled%20quarter-over-quarter%20for%20investors%20with%20more%20than%20%24500%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20dynamic%20appears%20to%20have%20continued%20going%20into%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%20this%20year%2C%20with%20large%20players%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblackstone-private-credit-earnings-schwarzman-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBlackstone%20reporting%20near-record%20private%20credit%3C%2Fa%3E%20fundraising%20from%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a30a2a62-5308-45c3-9a04-594a5b32efba%5C%22%3EAsset%20classes%20that%20are%20winning%20investor%20cash%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20asset%20class%20in%20the%20dataset%20to%20record%20net%20inflows%20from%20investors%20was%20infrastructure%2C%20with%20%241.38%20billion.%20The%20data%20is%20sourced%20from%20Canoe's%20500%2B%20institutional%20clients%20and%20is%20not%20a%20census%20of%20the%20entire%20alternatives%20market%2C%20but%20provides%20directional%20trends%20about%20allocation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20quarter%20had%20the%20largest%20total%20infrastructure%20contributions%2C%20%245.68%20billion%2C%20that%20Canoe%20has%20recorded%20since%20launching%20this%20report%20six%20quarters%20ago.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-private-equity-chasing-data-center-opportunity-blackstone-ares-apollo-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edigital%20infrastructure%20bet%20is%20likely%20driving%20this%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20shown%20by%20the%20popularity%20of%20the%20highly%20stable%20%26quot%3Bcore-plus%26quot%3B%20strategy%2C%20which%20combines%20relatively%20low-risk%2C%20income-generating%20bets%20with%20smaller%20allocations%20to%20riskier%20assets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInfrastructure%20Core%20Plus%2C%20the%20strategy%20that%20has%20driven%20net%20inflows%20for%20four%20straight%20quarters%2C%20is%20built%20around%20operational%2C%20contracted%2C%20long-duration%20assets%2C%26quot%3B%20Muniz%20said.%20%26quot%3BData%20centers%20fit%20that%20profile%20precisely.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20data%20can't%20be%20conclusively%20tied%20to%20individual%20assets%2C%20Muniz%20said%2C%20the%20pattern%20of%20steady%20capital%20flow%20that%20accelerated%20through%202025%20leaves%20little%20doubt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20be%20surprised%20if%20it%20were%20anything%20else%2C%26quot%3B%20Muniz%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221014%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Canoe%20Intelligence's%20chart%20showing%20quarterly%20contributions%20and%20distributions%20for%20infrastructure%20investors.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a039cdd58810e27922acfe9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22699%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20chart%20shows%20the%20quarterly%20cash%20flows%20for%20institutional%20investors%20in%20infrastructure.%3Cp%3ECanoe%20Intelligence%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20asset%20classes%20that%20have%20grown%20their%20share%20of%20investors'%20portfolios%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmay-hedge-fund-performance-millennium-citadel-schonfeld-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehedge%20funds%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20up%20from%2015%25%20of%20net%20value%20in%20mid-2024%20to%2022%25%20last%20quarter%2C%20and%20venture%20capital%2C%20which%20has%20overtaken%20private%20credit%20in%20the%20size%20of%20institutional%20portfolios%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20Canoe's%20dataset.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstitutional%20%26quot%3Ballocators%20are%20leaning%20in%2C%20not%20pulling%20back%26quot%3B%20in%20venture%20capital%2C%20said%20Muniz.%20Yes%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fso-much-money-that-its-hard-for-to-keep-up-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eboom%20in%20AI%20startups%20surely%20plays%20a%20part%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20investors%20are%20making%20a%20%26quot%3Bvintage-year%20decision%2C%26quot%3B%20betting%20that%20the%20current%20startup%20market%20will%20present%20some%20winning%20investment%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20capital%20is%20moving%2C%26quot%3B%20Muniz%20said.%20%26quot%3BLPs%20are%20choosing%20to%20be%20in%20the%20room.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhere-institutional-investors-are-putting-their-money-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778666401000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a03799558810e27922acd6c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhere-institutional-investors-are-putting-their-money-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Institutional%20investors%20are%20putting%20less%20money%20in%20private%20debt%20and%20more%20in%20venture%20and%20hedge%20funds%2C%20according%20to%20a%20Canoe%20Intelli