3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMarisela%20Cerda%2C%20who's%20worked%20at%20Microsoft%20for%20nearly%2025%20years%2C%20received%20a%20buyout%20offer%20at%20age%2047.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20company's%20offer%20has%20prompted%20her%20to%20consider%20her%20career%20and%20future%20contributions%20in%20tech.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECerda%20values%20Microsoft's%20culture%20under%20CEO%20Satya%20Nadella.%20It's%20one%20reason%20she%20stayed%20so%20long.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMarisela%20Cerda%2C%2047%2C%20is%20a%20principal%20customer%20experience%20manager%20at%20Microsoft%20and%20a%20former%20co-lead%20of%20the%20Women%20at%20Microsoft%20employee%20resource%20group.%20She%20started%20at%20the%20company%20in%202001%20and%2C%20because%20of%20her%20age%20and%20tenure%2C%20received%20a%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-internal-document-shows-buyout-offers-to-us-employees-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Evoluntary%20retirement%20offer%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0that%20would%20take%20effect%20in%20July.%20Business%20Insider%20verified%20her%20identity%20and%20employment.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20brevity%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20joined%20Microsoft%20right%20out%20of%20college%2C%20and%20I've%20been%20here%20over%20half%20my%20life.%20I%20had%20envisioned%20myself%20leaving%20at%20some%20point%2C%20but%20June%20wasn't%20in%20my%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20in%20my%20late%2040s%2C%20and%20in%20tech%2C%20that's%20like%20grandma%20age.%20It's%20on%20the%20verge%20of%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20not%20a%20senior%20executive%2C%20what%20are%20you%20doing%20in%20this%20industry%3F%26quot%3B%20I%20envision%20it%20being%20harder%20to%20find%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flaid-off-find-job-retirement-savings-ageism-linkedin-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ejob%20in%20my%2050s%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Plus%2C%20t%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-aging-ai-reshaping-job-market-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehe%20job%20market%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20not%20been%20easy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20this%2C%20I%20wasn't%20thinking%20about%20my%20age%20at%20all.%20Maybe%20that%20was%20my%20mistake.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThinking%20about%20retirement%20always%20felt%20like%20something%20far%20off%20in%20the%20future.%20Suddenly%2C%20this%20offer%20pulled%20that%20timeline%20into%20my%20late%2040s%2C%20and%20I%20wasn't%20ready%20for%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20I'm%20thinking%20about%20my%20life%20in%20a%20more%20finite%20way.%20You%20start%20asking%20yourself%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat's%20the%20difference%20I%20want%20to%20make%20in%20the%20world%3F%20What%20do%20I%20want%20to%20leave%20behind%20for%20my%20family%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225a286aaf-6711-45b4-ae96-1dc94abfd6b4%5C%22%3ENow%20what%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20moment%20has%20forced%20me%20to%20face%20those%20questions%20sooner%20than%20I%20thought%20I%20would.%20I%20knew%20I%20was%20going%20to%20reach%20my%2025-year%20mark%20at%20Microsoft%20in%20July%2C%20which%20is%20kind%20of%20a%20big%20deal.%20There's%20a%20wall%20of%20crystal%20plaques.%20And%20if%20you%20make%20it%20to%2025%20years%2C%20you%20get%20your%20name%20up%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20knew%20that%20when%20I%20hit%20that%20milestone%2C%20the%20next%20question%20would%20be%20%26quot%3BNow%20what%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20money%20they're%20offering%20brings%20no%20clarity%20to%20that%20question%20%E2%80%94%20only%20a%20sense%20of%20urgency.%20Because%20when%20it%20surfaced%2C%20it%20was%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%20my%20gosh%2C%20I'm%20included%20now%20in%20a%20category%20of%20people%20that%20are%20considered%20old.%26quot%3B%20The%20company%20would%20never%20say%20we're%20considered%20old%2C%20but%20it's%20brought%20my%20age%20to%20the%20top%20of%20my%20brain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20your%20career%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Atparadis%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etparadis%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20I'm%20already%20included%20in%20the%20retiree%20group%20at%2047%2C%20what%20does%20that%20mean%20for%2050%3F%20What%20does%2055%20look%20like%3F%20What's%20really%20bubbled%20up%20for%20me%20is%3A%20I'd%20better%20figure%20this%20out%2C%20because%20there%20does%20come%20a%20point%20where%20it%20gets%20harder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20buyout%20offer%20has%20accelerated%20the%20need%20to%20figure%20out%20what's%20next%2C%20how%20I'm%20going%20to%20spend%20my%20time%20for%20the%20next%2015%20years%20of%20my%20career%2C%20and%20to%20really%20home%20in%20on%20where%20I%20want%20to%20make%20a%20difference%20in%20my%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226ee782ac-4a4a-499b-b540-181d361263e9%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20don't%20feel%20so%20lost%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20get%20into%20our%20late%20career%2C%20this%20is%20the%20time%20we%20have%20the%20most%20experience%2C%20the%20most%20knowledge.%20I%20have%20the%20highest%20ability%20I've%20had%20at%20any%20time%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20things%20that%20are%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20your%20career%2C%20you%20go%20through%20lots%20of%20cycles%20of%20learning%2C%20and%20then%20eventually%20you're%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BEven%20with%20this%20changing%20environment%2C%20and%20even%20with%20AI%20being%20this%20whole%20new%20thing%20for%20the%20industry%2C%20for%20once%2C%20I%20don't%20feel%20so%20lost.%20I%20feel%20like%20I%20can%20figure%20this%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20very%20odd%20thing%20to%20experience.%20I'm%20more%20upbeat%20about%20my%20personal%20journey%20and%20where%20I%20need%20to%20go.%20I%20have%20more%20clarity%20for%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2273127c14-2fc4-4f9e-9413-3001fe11d81f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMove%20toward%20what%20you%20want%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20stayed%20as%20long%20as%20I%20stayed%20because%20Satya%20%5BNadella%5D%20became%20CEO%20in%202014%20and%20changed%20the%20culture%2C%20which%20really%20made%20it%20feel%20like%20a%20new%20company.%20Before%2C%20it%20was%20very%20in-your-face%20aggressive.%20The%20culture%20he%20set%20for%20us%20felt%20unique.%20It%20was%20about%20having%20a%20growth%20mindset%2C%20about%20valuing%20what%20our%20customers%20were%20telling%20us%2C%20about%20learning%20from%20mistakes%2C%20and%20being%20inclusive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20thinking%20about%20this%20possible%20transition%20for%20me%2C%20it's%20not%20just%20money%20I%20might%20leave%20on%20the%20table%2C%20but%20the%20next%20wave%20of%20technologies%20coming%20in%20that%20you%20miss%20out%20on%20learning%20about%20the%20same%20way.%20And%20you're%20at%20a%20company%20that%20invests%20billions%20of%20dollars%20in%20new%20technology%2C%20so%20where%20would%20it%20be%20better%20to%20learn%20it%20than%20here%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20about%20this%20a%20lot%20in%20my%20career%3A%20You%20move%20toward%20what%20you%20want%20more%20of%2C%20versus%20moving%20away%20from%20things%20you%20don't%20want.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20was%20walking%20through%20campus%20recently%2C%20I%20was%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BIs%20this%20one%20of%20the%20last%20times%20I'm%20going%20to%20be%20doing%20this%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20imagine%20myself%20on%20that%20day%2C%20having%20walked%20away%2C%20and%20it%20feels%20yucky%20because%20I%20think%20about%20the%20people%20I%20work%20with%2C%20and%20that%20I'm%20not%20going%20to%20jump%20on%20a%20call%20with%20them%20on%20a%20Monday%20like%20I%20normally%20would.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20really%20do%20think%20about%20it%20more%20than%20just%20my%20paycheck.%20I%20think%20about%20what%20kind%20of%20technological%20world%20I%20am%20leaving%20for%20my%20kids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20Hispanic.%20I%20grew%20up%20in%20Northern%20California%20when%20very%20few%20Latinos%20went%20into%20tech.%20I%20wanted%20other%20people%20to%20see%20that%20they%20could%20do%20it%2C%20too.%20I'm%20very%20grateful%20that%20I%20had%20this%20opportunity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EA%20Microsoft%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20buyout%20offer%20is%20voluntary.%20The%20program%20uses%20a%20formula%20based%20on%20age%20and%20years%20of%20service%20to%20cover%20longtime%20employees%20and%20those%20considering%20retirement.%20It%20includes%20added%20benefits%2C%20such%20as%20access%20to%20Microsoft%20health%20insurance%20for%20five%20years.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-buyout-offer-tech-career-reflection-at-age-47-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778665501000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a024fbfc9dd4cb81cda95c7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-buyout-offer-tech-career-reflection-at-age-47-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Marisela%20Cerda%20received%20a%20buyout%20offer%20from%20Microsoft%20after%20nearly%2025%20years%20at%20the%20company.%20At%2047%2C%20she%20hadn't%20started%20to%20consider%20when%20she'd%20retire.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tparadis%40businessinsider.com%20(Tim%20Paradis)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NDTV%20Exclusive%3A%20How%20Mediator%20Pakistan%20Has%20Been%20Harbouring%20Iranian%20Military%20Jets%20For%20Years%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Ciframe%20data-src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fembed-player%2Fid%2F1098688%2Fplay-via-app-wap%3FpWidth%3D100%26amp%3BpHeight%3D100%26amp%3Bembed_type%3Dstory%26amp%3Bsite%3Dclassic%26amp%3Bautostart%3D1%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22about%3Ablank%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%3E%2