%20sees%20trouble%20ahead%20for%20the%20US%2C%20Europe%2C%20and%20Japan%20unless%20corrective%20action%20is%20taken%20soon.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BThree%20of%20Europe's%20four%20largest%20economies%20are%20drowning%20in%20debt%2C%26quot%3B%20Lachman%20said%2C%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EEconomist%20Desmond%20Lachman%20thinks%20the%20US%20is%20facing%20a%20bond%20market%20crisis%3B%20he%20thinks%20several%20other%20leading%20economies%20are%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20International%20Monetary%20Fund%20director%20now%20serves%20as%20a%20senior%20fellow%20at%20the%20American%20Enterprise%20Institute%2C%20an%20economic%20policy%20think%20tank.%20He%20recently%20addressed%20the%20bond%20market%20crisis%20he%20sees%20brewing%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aei.org%2Feconomics%2Fbrewing-government-bond-market-crises%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblog%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20noting%20that%20%248.5%20trillion%20of%20outstanding%20US%20Treasury%20bonds%20are%20currently%20held%20by%20foreign%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20would%20seem%20to%20set%20the%20country%20up%20for%20a%20government%20bond%20market%20crisis%20should%20foreigners%20come%20to%20believe%20that%20the%20US%20was%20on%20the%20way%20to%20inflate%20its%20way%20out%20of%20its%20debt%20problem%20or%20that%20the%20US%20could%20further%20weaponize%20financial%20policy%2C%26quot%3B%20Lachman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20the%20yield%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbond-yields-30-year-treasury-inflation-stock-market-outlook-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E30-year%20US%20Treasury%20bond%3C%2Fa%3E%20rose%20above%205%25%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20nearly%20a%20year%2C%20driven%20by%20inflation%20and%20rate%20hike%20concerns.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20recently%2C%20JPMorgan%20Private%20Bank%20warned%20investors%20that%20if%20inflation%20remains%20sticky%2C%20it%20may%20pose%20complications%20for%20both%20stock%20and%20bond%20markets.%20A%20report%20from%20the%20bank%20drew%20parallels%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-inflation-interest-rates-outlook-bonds-bear-market-026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Einflation%20crisis%20%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20the%201970s%2C%20which%20led%20to%20a%20bear%20market%20for%20bonds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20Lachman%20noted%2C%20the%20brewing%20bond%20market%20crisis%20isn't%20confined%20to%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThree%20of%20Europe's%20four%20largest%20economies%20are%20drowning%20in%20debt%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhile%20in%202010%20the%20Eurozone%20debt%20crisis%20was%20centered%20on%20Portugal%2C%20Ireland%2C%20Italy%2C%20Greece%2C%20and%20Spain%2C%20Today%20it%20is%20France%2C%20Italy%2C%20and%20the%20United%20Kingdom%20about%20which%20we%20need%20to%20be%20worried.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20economist%20added%20that%20all%20three%20European%20nations%20have%20a%20public%20debt%20to%20GDP%20ratio%20that%20exceeds%20100%25%2C%20and%20each%20one%20is%20running%20a%20budget%20deficit%20of%20at%20least%205%25.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELachman%20noted%20that%20it%20could%20be%20thrown%20into%20recession%20by%20the%20series%20of%20ongoing%20shocks%20in%20energy%20and%20food%20markets.%20That%20said%2C%20he%20sees%20similar%20problems%20developing%20in%20one%20of%20Asia's%20top%20economies.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20a%20public%20debt%20to%20GDP%20ratio%20of%20around%20230%20percent%20and%20an%20expected%20primary%20budget%20deficit%2C%20Japan%20appears%20to%20be%20well%20on%20the%20way%20to%20a%20bond%20market%20crisis.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Lachman's%20view%2C%20the%20rise%20in%20the%2010-year%20Japanese%20government%20bond%20yield%20from%200.75%25%20to%202.5%25%2C%20its%20highest%20point%20in%20twenty%20years%2C%20is%20highly%20concerning.%20He%20also%20cited%20Japan's%20high%20vulnerability%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firan-war-oil-price-shock-commentary-bob-mcnally-nightmare-forecast-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eoil%20shocks%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20Iran%20war%20as%20another%20pain%20point.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20believes%20corrective%20measures%20are%20necessary%20in%20the%20US%2C%20Europe%2C%20and%20Japan%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%20to%20prevent%20a%20global%20bond%20market%20crisis%20from%20unfolding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20urgency%20of%20the%20need%20for%20such%20action%20is%20underlined%20by%20the%20fact%20that%20there%20appears%20to%20be%20government%20bond%20market%20problems%20brewing%20in%20each%20of%20these%20three%20major%20economies%20and%20that%20could%20have%20contagion%20effects%20should%20a%20bond%20market%20crisis%20occur%20in%20any%20of%20these%20economies%2C%26quot%3B%20Lachman%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbond-market-crisis-treasurys-iran-war-us-europe-japan-oil-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778665201000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0375ea7c7e83f26041ae0b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbond-market-crisis-treasurys-iran-war-us-europe-japan-oil-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Economist%20Desmond%20Lachman%20thinks%20corrective%20fiscal%20measures%20are%20needed%20from%20major%20economies%20to%20avoid%20a%20bond-market%20crisis.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sobrient%40insider.com%20(Samuel%20O'Brient)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Lyft%20says%20its%20latest%20AI%20push%20is%20all%20about%20helping%20drivers%20make%20more%20money%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20white-and-pink%20Lyft%20sticker%20sits%20on%20the%20inside%20of%20a%20car's%20rear%20windshield.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a023901c9dd4cb81cda94f3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELyft%20has%20rolled%20out%20its%20AI-based%20Earnings%20Assistant%20tool%20over%20the%20past%20year.%3Cp%3EBloomberg%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ELyft's%20AI%20tool%2C%20Earnings%20Assistant%2C%20offers%20drivers%20tips%20on%20where%20and%20when%20to%20drive.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20gives%20drivers%20another%20tool%20to%20maximize%20their%20earnings%20in%20a%20competitive%20industry.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20tool%20aims%20to%20help%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmedical-student-shares-uber-lyft-side-hustle-gig-work-struggles-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eboth%20new%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20experienced%20drivers%20maximize%20earnings.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdriven-for-uber-decade-dont-know-what-my-future-holds-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ERide-hailing%20drivers%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20spend%20months%20or%20years%20learning%20the%20best%20ways%20to%20make%20money.%20Now%2C%20there's%20artificial%20intelligence%20for%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELyft%20has%20been%20rolling%20out%20over%20the%20past%20year%20Earnings%20Assistant%2C%20a%20AI%20tool%20that%20gives%20drivers%20tips%20on%20where%20and%20when%20to%20drive.%20It%20shows%20how%20the%20company%20hopes%20to%20use%20AI%20to%20help%20drivers%20earn%20more%20in%20an%20industry%20where%20they're%20paid%20per%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tool%20has%20two%20features.%20One%2C%20called%20plan%20guidance%2C%20gives%20drivers%20advice%20on%20where%20to%20go%20to%20increase%20their%20chances%20of%20claiming%20rides%2C%20especially%20if%20they're%20planning%20to%20work%20on%20the%20app%20for%20a%20limited%20time.%20The%20option%2C%20available%20to%20drivers%20in%20the%20US%2C%20is%20meant%20to%20help%20new%20drivers%20find%20productive%20areas%20and%20times%20to%20work%2C%20a%20Lyft%20senior%20software%20engineer%2C%20Xiaoyi%20Duan%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20feature%2C%20called%20real-time%20guidance%2C%20pinpoints%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewhere%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-lyft-fares-rose-2025-riders-say-theyre-cutting-back-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ELyft%20customers%3C%2Fa%3E%20need%20rides.%20Lyft%20is%20still%20testing%20this%20feature%2C%20which%20is%20live%20in%20a%20few%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22750%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screenshot%20shows%20Lyft's%20Earnings%20Assistant%20feature%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a03438258810e27922acb2e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221624%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELyft's%20Earnings%20Assistant%20feature%20shows%20drivers%20where%20they%20can%20go%20to%20claim%20rides.%3Cp%3ELyft%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDrivers%20want%20to%20earn%20more%2C%20and%20they%20see%20various%20signals%20in%20the%20app%2C%20but%20those%20signals%20are%20not%20tailored%20to%20drivers'%20personalized%20needs%2C%26quot%3B%20Duan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELyft%20is%20using%20AI%20to%20synthesize%20the%20information%20%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%94%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Esuch%20as%20where%20ride%20requests%20are%20coming%20in%20or%20when%20they%20tend%20to%20spike%20in%20certain%20areas%20%E2%80%94%20and%20make%20personalized%20recommendations.%20That%20could%20mean%20pointing%20a%20driver%20toward%20a%20stadium%20when%20a%20concert%20is%20about%20to%20end%20or%20suggesting%20they%20pick%20up%20their%20last%20ride%20of%20the%20day%20at%20an%20airport%20because%20it's%20the%20busiest%20time%20of%20day%20for%20arrivals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELyft%20and%20rival%20Uber%20each%20have%20millions%20of%20drivers%20globally%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20accept%20rides%20on%20both%20services%2C%20comparing%20the%20pay%20and%20features.%20Uber%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fopenai.com%2Findex%2Fuber%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebeta-testing%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20similar%20AI%20feature%20to%20help%20drivers%20earn%20more%20on%20its%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERide-hailing%20drivers%20often%20learn%20how%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretired-wall-street-trader-drives-for-uber-lyft-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emaximize%20earnings%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20apps%20like%20Lyft%20and%20Uber%20as%20they%20gain%20experience.%20With%20millions%20of%20other%20people%20on%20the%20apps%2C%20though%2C%20claiming%20trips%20and%20making%20money%20can%20be%20competitive.%20And%20with%20no%20clear%20bosses%20or%20colleagues%2C%20figuring%20out%20how%20to%20make%20money%20on%20the%20apps%20is%20challenging.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELyft%20created%20Earnings%20Assistant%20within%20the%20past%20two%20years%2C%20the%20company%20said.%20The%20company%20showed%20early%20versions%20of%20the%20tool%20to%20drivers%20at%20events%20in%20Dallas%2C%20Las%20Vegas%2C%20and%20Miami%20last%20fall.%20It%20also%20tested%20Earnings%20Assistant%20with%20drivers%20who%20offered%20rides%20near%20Santa%20Clara%2C%20California%2C%20for%20February's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsuper-bowl-showcases-best-sort-workplace-revenge-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESuper%20Bowl%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20testing%20showed%20that%20experienced%20drivers%20often%20know%20to%20look%20for%20patterns%20that%20could%20help%20them%20earn%20more%20money%2C%20so%20they%20want%20more%20tips%20about%20where%20to%20go%20in%20the%20moment%2C%20Yuko%20Yamazaki%2C%20vice%20president%20and%20head%20of%20driver%20at%20Lyft%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20new%20Lyft%20drivers%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20are%20initially%20overwhelmed%20by%20the%20options%20when%20they%20start%20using%20the%20app%2C%20Yamazaki%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20Yamazaki%20said%20the%20app's%20plan%20guidance%20focuses%20on%20these%20drivers%20and%20offers%20suggestions%20on%20where%20to%20work%2C%20such%20as%2C%20%26quot%3BHere%20is%20what%20the%20next%20two%20hours%20could%20look%20like.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20real-time%20signals%20are%20becoming%20more%20of%20an%20interest%20for%20drivers%20as%20they%20become%20more%20mature%20on%20our%20platform%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuan%20said%20Lyft%20wants%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eto%20expand%20the%20tool%2C%20which%20currently%20requires%20drivers%20to%20prompt%20it%20for%20suggestions.%20Future%20iterations%20could%20tell%20drivers%20they're%20near%20a%20busy%20event%20as%20they%20pass%20it%2C%20or%20indicate%20how%20the%20weather%20is%20affecting%20opportunities%20to%20make%20money%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20trying%20to%20build%20an%20AI%20product%20because%20we%20want%20to%20use%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20Duan%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20trying%20to%20find%20what%20are%20the%20actual%20driver%20needs.%20That's%20the%20fundamental%20thing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20Lyft%2C%20Uber%2C%20or%20another%20ride-hailing%20service%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aabitter%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eabitter%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20via%20encrypted%20messaging%20app%20Signal%20at%20808-854-4501.%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%2C%20a%20nonwork%20WiFi%20network%2C%20and%20a%20nonwork%20device%3B%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehere's%20our%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-guide-to-securely-sharing-whistleblower-information-about-powerful-institutions-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eguide%20to%20sharing%20information