%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fc8beac9dd4cb81cda8065%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20said%20she%20regrets%20not%20building%20her%20own%20life%20when%20she%20first%20moved%20to%20New%20Zealand%20for%20love.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Ashlyn%20Oswalt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAfter%20navigating%20a%20long-distance%20relationship%20for%20a%20year%2C%20I%20took%20the%20leap%20and%20moved%20to%20New%20Zealand.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20got%20my%20happily%20ever%20after%2C%20but%20lost%20a%20bit%20of%20myself%20in%20the%20process.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIf%20I%20had%20it%20to%20do%20over%2C%20I'd%20do%20some%20things%20differently.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20met%20CJ%20at%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhostels-solo-travel-vacation-budget-travel-accommodation-airbnb-hotel-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMontreal%20hostel%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20didn't%20expect%20to%20purchase%20a%20one-way%20ticket%20to%20New%20Zealand%20around%20a%20year%20later.%20But%20after%20months%20of%20enduring%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flong-distance-relationship-lessons-trust-communication-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elong-distance%20relationship%3C%2Fa%3E%20between%20Chicago%20and%20Toronto%20(where%20he%20was%20living%20at%20the%20time)%2C%20and%20falling%20deeply%20in%20love%2C%20I%20chose%20the%20path%20of%20least%20resistance%3A%20a%20New%20Zealand%20work%20visa%20and%20a%20flight%20to%20Christchurch%2C%20CJ's%20hometown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20moved%20without%20a%20shred%20of%20research%2C%20convinced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-for-love-we-broke-up-i-stayed-turkey-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elove%20would%20be%20enough%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20build%20a%20personal%20foundation%20in%20a%20foreign%20country.%20I%20was%20in%20for%20a%20shock.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222448%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20and%20her%20now-husband%20take%20a%20picture%20of%20their%20reflection%20at%20the%20Cloud%20Gate%20in%20Chicago.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a032912e1443b8dc48e436c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221836%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20and%20her%20now-husband%20took%20their%20first%20photo%20together%20while%20seeing%20their%20reflection%20at%20the%20Cloud%20Gate%20in%20Chicago.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Ashlyn%20Oswalt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2252c597ea-f0ce-44e3-a1e5-31c5717c30ee%5C%22%3EI%20relied%20on%20my%20partner's%20social%20circle%2C%20instead%20of%20finding%20my%20own%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECJ%20grew%20up%20in%20Christchurch%2C%20and%20I%20lazily%20relied%20on%20his%20established%20group%20of%20mates%20to%20become%20my%20social%20circle.%20While%20they%20were%20lovely%2C%20our%20lives%20couldn't%20be%20more%20different.%20They%20were%20buying%20homes%20and%20having%20children%2C%20while%20CJ%20and%20I%20were%20still%20in%20the%20discovery%20phase%20of%20our%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEverything%20changed%20when%20I%20made%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmy-expat-friend-moved-away-and-it-broke-my-heart-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efirst%20American%20friend%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20bonded%20instantly%20over%20the%20things%20we%20missed%20from%20home%20and%20the%20friction%20of%20life%20here%2C%20and%20I%20finally%20felt%20seen.%20This%20relationship%20opened%20the%20door%20to%20my%20own%20community%2C%20and%20soon%20I%20had%20a%20group%20of%20people%20who%20knew%20me%20for%20me%2C%20not%20just%20as%20CJ's%20partner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221620%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20pets%20a%20sheep%20while%20holding%20a%20glass%20of%20wine.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0329deba7ef34b41f375b1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20admits%20that%20she%20relied%20too%20heavily%20on%20her%20partner's%20social%20circle%20when%20she%20first%20moved%20abroad.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Ashlyn%20Oswalt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22388a859c-23d6-440d-a467-aaa76b3c496b%5C%22%3EProfessional%20isolation%20seeped%20into%20every%20facet%20of%20my%20life%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20kept%20my%20remote%20US%20marketing%20job%20when%20I%20moved.%20Earning%20USD%20was%20great%2C%20but%20it%20meant%20I%20was%20physically%20in%20New%20Zealand%20while%20mentally%20and%20socially%20stuck%20on%20another%20continent.%20I%20had%20no%20reason%20to%20leave%20the%20house%2C%20no%20local%20colleagues%2C%20and%20nothing%20anchoring%20me%20to%20New%20Zealand%20%E2%80%94%20aside%20from%20CJ.%20That's%20a%20heck%20of%20a%20lot%20of%20pressure%20to%20put%20on%20a%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20I%20landed%20a%20copywriting%20role%20at%20a%20Kiwi%20outdoor%20brand.%20It%20was%20a%20dream%20job%20I'd%20struggled%20to%20find%20in%20the%20US.%20Being%20part%20of%20an%20iconic%20company%20connected%20me%20to%20my%20new%20home%20and%20provided%20me%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-canada-for-love-rebuild-my-career-identity-trailing-spouse-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprofessional%20identity%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20finally%20felt%20like%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22eecca6c9-56dc-4857-bee5-a4e6e5c97bee%5C%22%3EI%20focused%20on%20assimilation%20instead%20of%20identity%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20suppressed%20my%20%26quot%3BAmericanisms%26quot%3B%20for%20years%20%E2%80%94%20overenthusiasm%20and%20my%20love%20of%20country%20music%2C%20just%20to%20name%20a%20few%20%E2%80%94%20trying%20to%20fit%20in.%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20stick%20out%20like%20a%20sore%20thumb%2C%20but%20I%20was%20quietly%20destroying%20myself.%20I%20didn't%20bring%20my%20full%2C%20authentic%20self%20with%20me%20to%20New%20Zealand%2C%20and%20this%20was%20a%20reason%20for%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-us-to-paris-not-always-fairytale-homesick-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Econstant%20homesickness%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author's%20husband%20helps%20prepare%20to%20host%20a%20Thanksgiving%20dinner%20at%20their%20home%20in%20New%20Zealand.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a03297ae1443b8dc48e4373%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22608%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20said%20she%20tried%20to%20keep%20her%20American%20side%20quiet%20for%20many%20years.%20It%20wasn't%20until%20she%20embraced%20her%20true%20self%20and%20started%20doing%20things%20like%20hosting%20Thanksgiving%20that%20she%20could%20truly%20feel%20at%20home%20in%20New%20Zealand.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Ashlyn%20Oswalt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20years%2C%20but%20I%20slowly%20relearned%20who%20I%20was%2C%20sharing%20parts%20of%20my%20life%20I'd%20packed%20away.%20I%20hosted%20Thanksgiving%20dinners%20and%20threw%20country-music%20themed%20BBQs.%20I%20celebrated%20where%20I%20came%20from%2C%20and%20became%20comfortable%20with%20where%20I%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2258bd7951-b77e-4ed2-ae96-fe31cdb3e778%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20got%20my%20happily%20ever%20after%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20road%20to%20happily%20living%20in%20New%20Zealand%20was%20long%20and%20hard%2C%20but%20here%20I%20stand%2C%20at%20the%20other%20side.%20My%20own%20rom-com%20played%20out%20well%20in%20the%20end.%20My%20partner%20and%20I%20are%20happily%20married%20and%20settled%2C%20but%20I%20could%20have%20saved%20myself%20a%20lot%20of%20hardship%20if%20I%20had%20done%20things%20a%20bit%20differently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20do%20it%20all%20over%20again%2C%20but%20if%20I%20could%20give%20myself%20one%20piece%20of%20advice%2C%20I'd%20make%20sure%20I%20created%20my%20own%20life%20when%20I%20landed.%20Creating%20a