%20there%20are%20plenty%20of%20ways%20to%20keep%20the%20laptop%20awake%2C%20even%20if%20the%20lid%20is%20firmly%20shut.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAI%20is%20killing%20us%20if%20we%20don't%20know%20you%20can%20keep%20the%20laptop%20running%20while%20closed%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20commenter%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20some%20of%20people's%20suggested%20methods%20and%20workarounds%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ECaffeinate%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Some%20referenced%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Fhow-to-keep-mac-from-sleeping%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eterminal%20command%20%26quot%3Bcaffeinate%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20is%20designed%20to%20keep%20a%20MacBook%20from%20entering%20sleep%20mode%20while%2C%20say%2C%20giving%20a%20long%20presentation.%20This%20solution%20might%20be%20trickier%20for%20non-technical%20users%2C%20though.%20It%20could%20also%20drain%20your%20battery%20and%20require%20further%20terminal%20commands%20to%20get%20it%20to%20reliably%20work%20while%20the%20laptop%20lid%20is%20closed.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EClamshell%20Mode%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIf%20you%20plug%20your%20laptop%20into%20an%20external%20monitor%2C%20this%20setting%20lets%20you%20close%20the%20screen%20without%20it%20going%20to%20sleep.%20The%20only%20issue%2C%20of%20course%2C%20is%20that%20your%20computer%20needs%20to%20sense%20a%20connected%20device.%20For%20those%20on%20the%20move%2C%20ex-OpenAI%20staffer%20Will%20DePue%20half-jokingly%20recommended%20a%20dummy%20USB-C%20plug.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20nice%20to%20have%20physical%20control%20of%20whether%20your%20laptop%20is%20on!%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fwilldepue%2Fstatus%2F2053904970156789815%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehe%20wrote%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EChanging%20your%20sleep%20settings%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20In%20Mac's%20System%20Settings%2C%20users%20can%20adjust%20their%20sleep%20preferences.%20Ticking%20%26quot%3Bprevent%20automatic%20sleeping%20on%20power%20adapter%20when%20the%20display%20is%20off%26quot%3B%20may%20do%20the%20trick%2C%20but%20requires%20being%20plugged%20into%20a%20power%20source.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EAmphetamine%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20There's%20a%20handful%20of%20third-party%20software%20options%20that%20promise%20to%20keep%20your%20Mac%20running%20while%20shut.%20The%20most%20popular%20is%20likely%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-reverses-decision-ban-amphetamine-app-from-the-app-store-2021-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAmphetamine%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20keep-awake%20app%20for%20macOS.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20a%20host%20of%20other%20proposed%20tricks%3B%20go%20read%20the%20story's%20comments%20or%20the%20responses%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fupdate%2Furn%3Ali%3Aactivity%3A7459953366308323328%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eon%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fupdate%2Furn%3Ali%3Aactivity%3A7459961986869747714%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELinkedIn%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Several%20companies%20also%20offer%20cloud-based%20agents%2C%20though%20they%20can%20be%20more%20expensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20is%20also%20hinting%20that%20a%20solution%20for%20its%20Codex%20agent%20could%20be%20in%20the%20works%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20may%20be%20in%20for%20a%20treat%20soon%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20captioned%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40openai%2Fvideo%2F7636197889714244877%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20TikTok%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20the%20open-computer%20trend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20let's%20be%20real%3A%20life%20isn't%20always%20optimized.%20Sometimes%20you're%20running%20to%20the%20bus%20or%20catching%20a%20flight%2C%20and%20you%20don't%20know%20the%20exact%20command%20to%20use.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvibe-coding-build-apps-ai-market-flooded-killer-app-guy-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EVibe%20coders%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20also%20using%20these%20agents%2C%20and%20they%20may%20not%20know%20all%20the%20technical%20tips%20and%20tricks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20when%20an%20old-school%20method%20like%20keeping%20it%20cracked%20open%20can%20do%20the%20trick.%20Is%20it%20pretty%3F%20No.%20Does%20it%20work%20in%20a%20pinch%3F%20You%20betcha.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227a7a9a7e-cec0-4ac0-b3ab-cea35c9280fd%5C%22%3EChecking%20in%20with%20the%20open-laptop-walkers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20story's%20response%2C%20I%20checked%20back%20in%20with%20a%20handful%20of%20the%20open-laptop-walkers.%20Why%20didn't%20they%20use%20one%20of%20these%20hacks%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E10th%20grader%20Arav%20Jain%20wrote%20in%20an%20email%20that%20%26quot%3Bthere%20are%20tools%20like%20Amphetamine%20available%2C%20but%20I%20just%20found%20out%20about%20that%20yesterday.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUX%20designer%20Andreas%20Kruszakin-Liboska%20wrote%20that%20he%20%26quot%3Bdidn't%20know%26quot%3B%20about%20the%20tricks.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20too%20much%20friction.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%2C%20Kruszakin-Liboska%20wasn't%20interested%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-a-dongle-2013-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ein%20a%20dongle%3C%2Fa%3E%20sticking%20out%20of%20his%20computer%20to%20keep%20his%20agents%20running.%20His%20ideal%20hack%3A%20simple%2C%20clean%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bdoesn't%20disturb%20me%20from%20my%20busy%20enough%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGeoff%20Chan%20had%20recently%20learned%20about%20the%20settings%20changes%20and%20plug-ins.%20At%20a%20conference%2C%20he%20kept%20his%20laptop%20open%20a%20tad%20while%20using%20a%20coding%20agent%20on%20his%20phone.%20His%20wife%20and%20kids%20were%20there%2C%20and%20he%20told%20them%2C%20%26quot%3BDo%20not%20close%20the%20laptop.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20wife%20told%20him%20to%20change%20his%20settings%2C%20which%20he%20did.%20While%20the%20computer%20stayed%20active%20when%20closed%2C%20Chan%20said%20that%20it%20wouldn't%20stay%20connected%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwebsite-tests-hotel-wifi-2014-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehotel's%20WiFi%3C%2Fa%3E.%20A%20friend%20finally%20told%20him%20to%20download%20third-party%20software%2C%20which%20he%20said%20worked%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChan%20wasn't%20surprised%20by%20the%20story's%20active%20comments%20section.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20something%20there%20that%20hits%20a%20nerve%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20developers%20out%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20massive%20change%20happening%20to%20their%20jobs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22577c0b2d-bf65-49d6-bbeb-a04c369659ba%5C%22%3EHave%20you%20noticed%20other%20quirky%20behavior%20from%20AI%20coders%3F%20Take%20our%20survey%3A%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%2F%2Fembed.typeform.com%2Fnext%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20data-tf-live%3D%5C%2201KREQBAKERK41E043EN2GFDM8%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-keep-laptop-ai-agent-running-while-lid-closed-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778663702000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0383aa58810e27922ace57%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-keep-laptop-ai-agent-running-while-lid-closed-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Business%20Insider%20readers%20sounded%20off%20about%20techies%20walking%20around%20with%20laptops%20slightly%20open%20for%20their%20AI%20agents.%20Many%20recommended%20workarounds.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22hchandonnet%40insider.com%20(Henry%20Chandonnet)%22%2C%22e