ts%20are%20a%20powerhouse%20of%20complex%20carbohydrates%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sandhya.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20don%E2%80%99t%20just%20give%20energy%2C%20they%20also%20provide%20fibre%2C%20iron%2C%20and%20calcium.%20They%20support%20steady%20growth%2C%20bone%20strength%2C%20and%20even%20cognitive%20development%20in%20children.%20And%20for%20India%2C%20millets%20are%20a%20blessing%20because%20they%20grow%20easily%20in%20our%20soil.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanchita%20emphasises%20that%20the%20approach%20to%20millets%20matters%3A%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20introduce%20them%20in%20a%20child%E2%80%99s%20first%20foods%2C%20say%2C%20%3Cem%3Eragi%20%3C%2Fem%3Eporridge%20at%20seven%20months%2C%20they%20accept%20it%20as%20normal.%20But%20if%20you%20suddenly%20swap%20rice%20for%20jowar%20at%20age%20five%2C%20there%20will%20be%20resistance.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20I%20recommend%20to%20clients%20is%20that%20for%20the%20first%20two%20to%20three%20weeks%2C%20you%20start%20with%20just%20fruits%20and%20vegetables%20to%20let%20your%20child%20ease%20into%20solids.%20Around%20six%20and%20a%20half%20months%2C%20you%20can%20introduce%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F343315%2Fbiggest-millet-exporters-in-india-ra-foods-sisters-priya-akila-gunasekar-run-multi-crore-millet-business%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrains%20like%20%3Cem%3Eragi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20jowar%2C%20quinoa%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20rice%2C%20since%20they%20need%20the%20carbs.%20To%20make%20these%20easier%20to%20digest%2C%20you%20can%20soak%20them%20overnight%20in%20warm%20water%20or%20even%20with%20a%20little%20lemon%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20suggests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanchita%20also%20notes%20that%20millets%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20feel%20%E2%80%9Cboring%E2%80%9D%20or%20traditional.%20%E2%80%9CParents%20can%20make%20millet%20waffles%2C%20millet%20pizza%20bases%2C%20or%20even%20millet-based%20cookies.%20Kids%20respond%20better%20when%20the%20food%20looks%20familiar%20but%20is%20nutritionally%20upgraded.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-instagram%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDK9U1MqNhDE%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDK9U1MqNhDE%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDK9U1MqNhDE%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Roshini%20Daswani%20Kewalram%20%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22%F0%9F%92%8B%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fs.w.org%2Fimages%2Fcore%2Femoji%2F16.0.1%2F72x72%2F1f48b.png%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-smiley%5C%22%3E%20(%40roshinidaswani)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESandhya%2C%20also%20a%20lactation%20counsellor%2C%20highlights%20their%20role%20for%20mothers%20too%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20recommend%20%3Cem%3Eragi%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20expecting%20and%20breastfeeding%20mothers.%20It%E2%80%99s%20the%20richest%20source%20of%20calcium%20and%20even%20supports%20breast%20milk%20production.%20%3Cem%3EBajra%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20rich%20in%20iron%2C%20is%20another%20star.%20When%20mothers%20eat%20these%20grains%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20strengthening%20themselves%20and%20their%20babies%20simultaneously.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParents%20might%20worry%20about%20the%20cost%20of%20microgreens%20and%20millets%20%E2%80%94%20after%20all%2C%20trendy%20foods%20are%20often%20expensive%20(think%20avocados).%20But%20100%20gm%20of%20fresh%20microgreens%20straight%20from%20farms%20costs%20only%20Rs%20125%20to%20Rs%20135.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETackling%20the%20parent%20dilemma%3A%20Fussiness%2C%20time%20and%20trends%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20knowing%20the%20benefits%20and%20actually%20getting%20children%20to%20eat%20them%20are%20two%20very%20different%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CParents%20often%20tell%20me%2C%20%E2%80%98My%20child%20rejects%20everything%20except%20pasta%20and%20biscuits%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sandhya.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20trick%20is%20persistence%20and%20creativity.%20If%20a%20millet%20pancake%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20work%20one%20day%2C%20try%20millet%20%3Cem%3Eidli%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethe%20next%20%E2%80%94%20or%20millet%20cookies%2C%20chocolates%2C%20even%20burgers%20with%20millet%20patties.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20give%20up%20after%20one%20rejection.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanchita%20adds%20her%20practical%20hacks%3A%20%E2%80%9CIf%20your%20child%20loves%20pasta%2C%20swap%20the%20base%20for%20millet%20pasta%20%E2%80%94%20it%E2%80%99s%20available%20now.%20Or%20make%20the%20sauce%20more%20nutrient-rich%20by%20blending%20in%20spinach%2C%20pumpkin%2C%20or%20microgreens.%20You%20don%E2%80%99t%20always%20have%20to%20reinvent%20meals%2C%20just%20upgrade%20them.%20Take%20the%20foods%20they%20already%20like%20and%20make%20small%20changes.%20For%20example%2C%20add%20a%20pinch%20of%20spirulina%20to%20pancakes%2C%20make%20a%20%3Cem%3Eragi%20%3C%2Fem%3Echocolate%20popsicle%20or%20smoothie%2C%20or%20mix%20a%20spoon%20of%20amaranth%20seeds%20into%20rice.%20It%E2%80%99s%20the%20same%20colour%2C%20so%20they%20won%E2%80%99t%20even%20notice%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20experts%20agree%20that%20a%20fun%20presentation%20matters.%20A%20spinach%20%3Cem%3Edosa%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebecomes%20a%20%E2%80%98Hulk%20dosa%E2%80%99.%20An%20%3Cem%3Eidli%3C%2Fem%3E%20with%20%3Cem%3Echutney%3C%2Fem%3E%20eyes%20transforms%20into%20a%20bunny.%20Bento%20boxes%20%E2%80%94%20those%20colourful%2C%20compartmentalised%20lunch%20kits%20trending%20on%20Instagram%20%E2%80%94%20can%20also%20help%20make%20food%20visually%20exciting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-instagram%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDLALf0oSNdH%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDLALf0oSNdH%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDLALf0oSNdH%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Sanchita%20Mahtani%20%2F%20Baby%20%26amp%3B%20Toddler%20Nutrition%20Consultant%20(%40sanchitadaswani)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20first%20slipped%20millet%20cookies%20with%20cocoa%20powder%20into%20my%20son%E2%80%99s%20tiffin%2C%20I%20thought%20he%E2%80%99d%20trade%20them%20away.%20Instead%2C%20he%20came%20home%20asking%20if%20I%20could%20pack%20more%20the%20next%20day.%20It%E2%80%99s%20become%20his%20go-to%20snack%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ritu%20Sharma%2C%20a%20Delhi-based%20mother.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CNow%20I%E2%80%99ve%20slowly%20started%20experimenting%20with%20other%20changes.%20A%20sprinkle%20of%20home-grown%20microgreens%20on%20%3Cem%3Edal%20%3C%2Fem%3Eor%20%3Cem%3Erotis%3C%2Fem%3E%20seemed%20like%20nothing%20at%20first%2C%20but%20over%20time%20he%20began%20noticing%20the%20extra%20crunch.%20These%20days%2C%20he%20even%20reminds%20me%20if%20I%20forget%20to%20add%20them.%20It%E2%80%99s%20the%20little%20victories%20like%20this%20that%20make%20me%20feel%20reassured%20that%20he%E2%80%99s%20getting%20the%20right%20nutrition%20without%20the%20mealtime%20battles.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20working%20parents%2C%20time%20is%20a%20real%20hurdle.%20But%20Sandhya%20reassures%3A%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20now%20brands%20offering%20ready-to-make%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F336832%2Fias-officer-sushant-gaurav-transforms-gumla-district-of-jharkhand-with-ragi-millet%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emillet%20pancake%20mixes%20%3C%2Fa%3Eor%20%3Cem%3Edosa%3C%2Fem%3E%20flours.%20Just%20add%20milk%20and%20cook.%20But%20always%20check%20the%20labels.%20Choose%20products%20with%20minimal%20preservatives%20and%20zero%20palm%20oil.%20And%20above%20all%2C%20pre-plan.%20Weekly%20meal%20prep%20makes%20life%20easier.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5C